(48, 116, '體育博彩術語大全', '常用盤口的種類及輸贏的計算方法解釋', NULL, 1, 0, '<div class=\"product\">\r\n<article id=\"post-1493\" class=\"post-1493 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail  category-43 single-post-content \">\r\n						<div class=\"post-header post-tp-1-header\">\r\n									<h1 class=\"single-post-title\">\r\n						<span class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">體育博彩術語大全</span></h1>\r\n										<div class=\"post-meta-wrap clearfix\">\r\n						<div class=\"term-badges \"><span class=\"term-badge term-43\">玩運彩技巧教學</span></div>					</div>\r\n									<div class=\"single-featured\">\r\n									</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n						<div class=\"entry-content clearfix single-post-content\">\r\n				<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_22 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-light-blue\">\r\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\r\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">內容目錄</p>\r\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: inline;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"></i></a></span></div>\r\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"#%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%E5%8D%9A%E5%BD%A9%E8%A1%93%E8%AA%9E%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%A8\" title=\"體育博彩術語大全\">體育博彩術語大全</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"#%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%E5%8D%9A%E5%BD%A9%E8%B3%AD%E7%90%83%E8%A1%93%E8%AA%9E\" title=\" 體育博彩/賭球術語\"> 體育博彩/賭球術語</a><ul class=\"ez-toc-list-level-3\"><li class=\"ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"#%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E6%98%AF%E8%AE%93%E7%90%83%EF%BC%9F\" title=\" 什麼是讓球？\"> 什麼是讓球？</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"#%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E7%9B%A4%E5%8F%A3%E7%9A%84%E7%A8%AE%E9%A1%9E%E5%8F%8A%E8%BC%B8%E8%B4%8F%E7%9A%84%E8%A8%88%E7%AE%97%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8B\" title=\"常用盤口的種類及輸贏的計算方法解釋\">常用盤口的種類及輸贏的計算方法解釋</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"#%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E7%90%83%EF%BC%9F\" title=\"什麼是大小球？\">什麼是大小球？</a></li></ul></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-268f00cc-00ea-4b9c-81d7-04c4c60a036a\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%E5%8D%9A%E5%BD%A9%E8%A1%93%E8%AA%9E%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%A8\"></span><strong>體育博彩術語大全</strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-85434d75-f22c-4277-a08c-5d4d323c07fa\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>有無數鐵杆球迷，覆蓋範圍從足球到NBA等各類體育比賽，其中不少人愛好體育博彩/賭球，在某場比賽中花點小錢，買自己喜愛的球隊贏，給生活添了不少樂趣。本文介紹了體育博彩的相關術語、體育博彩技巧和優秀的體育博彩網站。<br><br></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-ba088d61-1a8f-4762-886e-7066619e6192\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%E5%8D%9A%E5%BD%A9%E8%B3%AD%E7%90%83%E8%A1%93%E8%AA%9E\"></span><strong> 體育博彩/賭球術語</strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-3e8ea6ab-e3b4-4a6d-b555-2bca993f0bb2\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E6%98%AF%E8%AE%93%E7%90%83%EF%BC%9F\"></span><strong><span class=\"tadv-color\" style=\"color: #0693e3;\"> 什麼是讓球？</span></strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>所謂“讓球”，就是指博彩公司根據對陣兩支球隊聯賽排名、實力對比、主客場因素、以往戰績比較、傷停情況等進行客觀分析，列出強隊向弱隊讓球的比例。“讓球比例”很大程度上反映了對陣雙方實力的強弱。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>以AC米蘭與切沃之戰為例，AC米蘭讓0．5，即半球，也就是說，如果雙方打平，買AC米蘭者算輸，因為0&lt;0．5。如果AC米蘭淨勝一球以上，買AC米蘭的人才算贏，因為1&gt;0．5。而切沃接受AC米蘭的讓球，就構成了“受讓”。讓球比例會隨著對陣雙方實力強弱而具體變化。如果主辦者認為AC米蘭1球取勝還不算贏，讓球比例會變化為“1”，“1／1．5”，“1．5”等，“1”表示AC米蘭淨勝一球，買他的人不輸不贏；“1／1．5”表示AC米蘭淨勝一球，競猜者算贏一半，淨勝兩球以上才全贏。“1．5”表明AC米蘭淨勝一球也算輸，必須淨勝兩球才算贏，受讓可以倒過來理解。通常最大的讓球比例可達到2．5，再多意義不大。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>仍以AC米蘭與切沃之戰為例，直觀的解釋如下：</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>1．半球 表示AC米蘭輸或平，買它的人輸掉全部錢；AC米蘭贏一個球以上（包括1球），全贏。<br>2．半球/一球 AC米蘭輸或平，買它的人全輸；AC米蘭勝一球，買AC米蘭的人贏一半；AC米蘭贏兩球，買它的人全贏<br>3．平手 意思是兩隊中哪支獲勝，買它的人就贏錢，買到負方球隊的人就輸錢。<br>4．平手/半球 AC米蘭輸了，買它的人全輸；AC米蘭打平，買它的人輸一半；AC米蘭贏一個球以上（包括一球），買它的人全贏。<br>5．一球 AC米蘭輸或平，買它的人全輸；AC米蘭若只勝一球，則為走盤，玩家除需要支付一定的手續費外，不輸不贏，AC米蘭勝兩球以上（包括兩球），買它的人全贏。<br>6．球半/兩球 AC米蘭輸或平，買它的人輸掉全部錢；AC米蘭贏一球，玩家也全輸。AC米蘭勝兩球，買它的人贏一半；AC米蘭勝兩球以上（不包括兩球），買它的人贏得全部錢…</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>什麼是盤口？所謂盤口，是流行在東南亞和我國港澳地區的一種足球博彩方式，由於大部分的足球比賽中客觀上存在些許的差距，那麼為了使得博奕更加刺激和公平，主持足球博奕的一方（通常稱為莊家）常常對比賽列出某隊和某隊之間的人為差距，但是為了使得最後的足球博奕產生輸贏結果，莊家會開出比賽中不存在，但是博奕中常見的0.5球的差距，比如像A隊做客B隊，A隊實力明顯在主隊B隊之上，如果沒有這樣的讓0.5球，那麼對於足球博奕的參與者和主持者來說，都是不公平的，因為這樣所有具備足球知識的人都會壓注A隊贏，就是打平也不至於輸，這對於莊家來說也是只輸不贏的。但是當把這0.5球首先加在B隊身上，那麼比賽還沒有開始，B隊就以0.5：0領先了（足球博奕上），如果這場比賽A隊不淨勝一球以上（包括打平），那麼不管比賽的結果如何，壓注B隊的球迷將從莊家那裡贏錢，反之如果A隊贏球，哪怕是1：0，那麼在比賽之外的足球博奕中，A隊就以1：0.5獲勝，壓注A隊的球迷就會贏錢。以此類推，莊家開出讓1球、1.5球甚至2球也是這樣計算博奕的輸贏，不過在讓球為整數的時候，比如A隊主場讓B隊一球，比賽的結果如果是A隊只淨勝一球，那麼這場比賽在博奕時候即沒有輸贏，因為加上莊家開出的一球，“比分”是平局。需要指出的是，目前公認的足球比賽的盤口是由澳門博彩公司開出的比賽盤口。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>注 亞洲讓球盤口的人基本有“全輸、輸一半、不輸不贏、贏一半、全贏”幾種結果。 什麼是水位？水位即比賽結果出來以後，博彩者的盈和輸的係數。<br>什麼是上下盤？ “上盤”是指讓球方，“下盤”是指被讓球方。<br><br></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-59f2ec80-1e54-437d-8446-db4a03582e46\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E7%9B%A4%E5%8F%A3%E7%9A%84%E7%A8%AE%E9%A1%9E%E5%8F%8A%E8%BC%B8%E8%B4%8F%E7%9A%84%E8%A8%88%E7%AE%97%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8B\"></span>常用盤口的種類及輸贏的計算方法解釋<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-7d2d842e-2874-4441-b474-ad798879a9f3\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>盤口(數字表示)&nbsp;&nbsp; 盤口解釋<br>平手(0)&nbsp;&nbsp; 雙方平開，雙方獲勝的幾率一樣<br>平手/半球(0/0.5)&nbsp; 讓球方打平買它的人輸一半，贏一個全贏<br>半球(0.5)&nbsp;&nbsp; 讓球方打平或者輸球買它的全輸，贏一個全贏<br>半球/一球(0.5/1)&nbsp; 讓球方平或負全輸，贏一球贏一半，贏兩球全贏<br>一球(1)&nbsp;&nbsp; 讓球方輸、平全輸，贏一個球算平，贏兩球全贏<br>一球/球半(1/1.5)&nbsp; 讓球方贏一個球買它的人輸一半，贏兩球全贏<br>球半(1.5)&nbsp;&nbsp; 讓球方輸、平、贏一個全輸，贏兩個球全贏<br>球半/兩球(1.5/2)&nbsp; 讓球方贏兩個買它的贏一半，贏三個全贏</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-49dd2964-5a7c-4c16-9eaa-a5adf515ccf8\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E7%90%83%EF%BC%9F\"></span>什麼是大小球？<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-004e8e39-bd57-4d8d-9aa0-cb00322be66b\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p><strong><span class=\"tadv-color\" style=\"color: #0693e3;\"> 小球：每場比賽(90分鐘內)進球小於3球</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span class=\"tadv-color\" style=\"color: #0693e3;\"> 大球：每場比賽(90分鐘內)進球等於或大於3球</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>1、計算方法<br>舉例子來說明，盤口是2.5球，所謂小球就是尤文和博洛尼亞兩隊在90分鐘比賽時間內的總入球數如果小於2.5球，則就是小球；所謂大球就是尤文和博洛尼亞兩隊在90分鐘比賽時間內的總入球數如果大於2.5球，則就是大球，上面例子的結果是2：1，也就是總入球數是3，大於2.5，所以就是大球。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>2、常用盤口的種類及解釋：<br>2球 兩隊總入球數小於2，則就是小球，贏整盤或輸整盤；兩隊總入球數大於2，則就是大球，贏整盤或輸整盤；兩隊總入球數等於2，就是走盤</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>2/2.5球 兩隊總入球數小於2，則就是小球，贏整盤或輸整盤;兩隊總入球數大於2.5，則就是大球，贏整盤或輸整盤;兩隊總入球數等於2，則壓小球者贏半盤，壓大球者輸半盤。 2.5球 兩隊總入球數小於2.5，則就是小球，贏整盤或輸整盤；兩隊總入球數大於2.5，則就是大球，贏整盤或輸整盤;不存在走盤…</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<!--codes_iframe--><!--/codes_iframe-->			</div>\r\n\r\n						</article>\r\n</div>', '2022-05-25 06:16:32'),
(49, 111, '個人足球博彩投注看盤心得', '足球博彩盤面解析', NULL, 1, 0, '<div class=\"product\">\r\n<article id=\"post-1706\" class=\"post-1706 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail  category-43 single-post-content \">\r\n						<div class=\"post-header post-tp-1-header\">\r\n									<h1 class=\"single-post-title\">\r\n						<span class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">個人足球博彩投注看盤心得</span></h1>\r\n										<div class=\"post-meta-wrap clearfix\">\r\n						<div class=\"term-badges \"><span class=\"term-badge term-43\">玩運彩技巧教學</span></div>					</div>\r\n									<div class=\"single-featured\">\r\n									</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n						<div class=\"entry-content clearfix single-post-content\">\r\n				<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_22 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-light-blue\">\r\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\r\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">內容目錄</p>\r\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: inline;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"></i></a></span></div>\r\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"#%E8%B6%B3%E7%90%83%E5%8D%9A%E5%BD%A9%E7%9B%A4%E9%9D%A2%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90\" title=\"足球博彩盤面解析\">足球博彩盤面解析</a><ul class=\"ez-toc-list-level-3\"><li class=\"ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"#%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81%E5%B9%B3%E6%89%8B%E7%9B%A4%EF%BC%9A\" title=\"一、平手盤：\">一、平手盤：</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"#%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%81%E5%B9%B3%E5%8D%8A%E7%9B%A4%EF%BC%9A\" title=\"二、平半盤：\">二、平半盤：</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"#%E4%B8%89%E3%80%81%E5%8D%8A%E7%90%83%E7%9B%A4%EF%BC%9A%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%8F%E6%8A%95%E6%B3%A8%E7%B6%B2%E9%96%8B%E6%88%B6\" title=\"三、半球盤：正規投注網開戶\">三、半球盤：正規投注網開戶</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"#%E5%9B%9B%E3%80%81%E5%8D%8A%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%A4%EF%BC%9A%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%8F%E6%8A%95%E6%B3%A8%E7%B6%B2%E9%96%8B%E6%88%B6\" title=\"四、半\\一盤：正規投注網開戶\">四、半\\一盤：正規投注網開戶</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"#%E4%BA%94%E3%80%81%E4%B8%80%E7%90%83%E7%9B%A4%EF%BC%9A\" title=\"五、一球盤：\">五、一球盤：</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"#%E5%85%AD%E3%80%81%E4%B8%80%E7%90%83%E7%90%83%E5%8D%8A%E7%9B%A4%EF%BC%9A\" title=\"六、一球\\球半盤：\">六、一球\\球半盤：</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"#%E4%B8%83%E3%80%81%E7%90%83%E5%8D%8A%E7%9B%A4%EF%BC%9A%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%8F%E6%8A%95%E6%B3%A8%E7%B6%B2%E9%96%8B%E6%88%B6\" title=\"七、球半盤：正規投注網開戶\">七、球半盤：正規投注網開戶</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"#%E5%85%AB%E3%80%81%E7%90%83%E5%8D%8A%E5%85%A9%E7%90%83%E7%9B%A4%EF%BC%9A%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%8F%E6%8A%95%E6%B3%A8%E7%B6%B2%E9%96%8B%E6%88%B6\" title=\"八、球半\\兩球盤：正規投注網開戶\">八、球半\\兩球盤：正規投注網開戶</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"#%E4%B9%9D%E3%80%81%E9%97%9C%E6%96%BC%E7%9B%A4%E5%8F%A3%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%8A%E5%8B%95%EF%BC%9A%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%8F%E6%8A%95%E6%B3%A8%E7%B6%B2%E9%96%8B%E6%88%B6\" title=\"九、關於盤口的變動：正規投注網開戶\">九、關於盤口的變動：正規投注網開戶</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"#%E5%8D%81%E3%80%81%E5%82%99%E8%A8%BB%EF%BC%9A%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%8F%E6%8A%95%E6%B3%A8%E7%B6%B2%E9%96%8B%E6%88%B6%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E7%9B%A4%E5%8F%A3%E5%9D%87%E7%82%BA%E5%88%9D%E7%9B%A4%E3%80%82\" title=\"十、備註：正規投注網開戶以上盤口均為初盤。\">十、備註：正規投注網開戶以上盤口均為初盤。</a></li></ul></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img width=\"70%\" class=\"wp-image-1732 b-loaded\" alt=\"足球博彩看盤心得\" srcset=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/_aol4_fdq3m-819x1024.jpg 819w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/_aol4_fdq3m-240x300.jpg 240w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/_aol4_fdq3m-768x960.jpg 768w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/_aol4_fdq3m.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 819px) 100vw, 819px\" src=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/_aol4_fdq3m-819x1024.jpg\">\r\n<figcaption>足球博彩心得</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-76d2ff46-d094-4286-b482-aada0e38ff34\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E8%B6%B3%E7%90%83%E5%8D%9A%E5%BD%A9%E7%9B%A4%E9%9D%A2%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90\"></span><strong>足球博彩盤面解析</strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-6dbdc526-e566-46f0-8d11-440c64775dad\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81%E5%B9%B3%E6%89%8B%E7%9B%A4%EF%BC%9A\"></span><span class=\"tadv-color\" style=\"color: #0693e3;\"><strong>一、平手盤：</strong></span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>莊家給出的平手盤一般都是雙方狀態實力比較接近的隊，這讓投注者比較難選擇，但是根據本人的統計平手盤大多數都會分出勝負，而且小球可以占到75%，因此本人建議平手盤多看看小球，除非有確切的把握選擇，另外平手盤大家也可以看看歐賠，大部分平手盤的歐賠都是2.3.2的組合這樣在平手盤大多數都會分出勝負的情況下，大家不妨去掉平局選擇兩頭，在均注的情況下會有收穫的。正規投注網開戶</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%81%E5%B9%B3%E5%8D%8A%E7%9B%A4%EF%BC%9A\"></span><span class=\"tadv-color\" style=\"color: #0693e3;\"><strong>二、平半盤：</strong></span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>莊家給出的平半盤一般都是一方狀態實力稍微好于另一方或有主場之利，因此有很多投注者都會選擇上盤，然而根據本人的統計，平半盤大多都會是平局結尾，下盤有很大的抱冷希望，因此本人建議平半盤多注意踢平。正規投注網開戶</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E4%B8%89%E3%80%81%E5%8D%8A%E7%90%83%E7%9B%A4%EF%BC%9A%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%8F%E6%8A%95%E6%B3%A8%E7%B6%B2%E9%96%8B%E6%88%B6\"></span><span class=\"tadv-color\" style=\"color: #0693e3;\"><strong>三、半球盤：正規投注網開戶</strong></span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>半球盤是生死盤裡最難選擇的一個，在我個人的統計中上下盤各50%,但由平半升為半球的(不包括臨場1小時升盤)上盤跑出的概率還是很大的,在對付半球盤時請大家注意！！另外半球盤的大球出的較多.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E5%9B%9B%E3%80%81%E5%8D%8A%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%A4%EF%BC%9A%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%8F%E6%8A%95%E6%B3%A8%E7%B6%B2%E9%96%8B%E6%88%B6\"></span><span class=\"tadv-color\" style=\"color: #0693e3;\"><strong>四、半\\一盤：正規投注網開戶</strong></span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>半\\一盤是我個人比較喜歡的盤，個人統計上盤出的機率比較大，但容易變盤使人迷惑，在半\\一盤所對應的歐賠範圍內，有一些是不穩定的，所以在半\\一盤時請對應歐賠比較，半\\一升一球(不包括臨場1小時升盤)上盤55%走盤30%下盤15%。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E4%BA%94%E3%80%81%E4%B8%80%E7%90%83%E7%9B%A4%EF%BC%9A\"></span><span class=\"tadv-color\" style=\"color: #0693e3;\"><strong>五、一球盤：</strong></span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>本人認為一球盤大球出的機率很大，一球盤走盤占50%，但臨場為一球的盤口很少，大部分都變盤，所以請大家自己把握。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E5%85%AD%E3%80%81%E4%B8%80%E7%90%83%E7%90%83%E5%8D%8A%E7%9B%A4%EF%BC%9A\"></span><span class=\"tadv-color\" style=\"color: #0693e3;\"><strong>六、一球\\球半盤：</strong></span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>個人認為這個盤口是報冷的主要盤口，大部分出下盤約占70%，屬於贏球輸盤的重點盤口，尤其是由一球盤升盤的，這樣的盤不妨投歐賠。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E4%B8%83%E3%80%81%E7%90%83%E5%8D%8A%E7%9B%A4%EF%BC%9A%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%8F%E6%8A%95%E6%B3%A8%E7%B6%B2%E9%96%8B%E6%88%B6\"></span><span class=\"tadv-color\" style=\"color: #0693e3;\"><strong>七、球半盤：正規投注網開戶</strong></span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>與一球\\球半盤正好相反，是上盤比較容易出，莊家給出這樣的盤口基本上是兩隊實力的反映，而且臨場很少變盤，比較穩定。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E5%85%AB%E3%80%81%E7%90%83%E5%8D%8A%E5%85%A9%E7%90%83%E7%9B%A4%EF%BC%9A%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%8F%E6%8A%95%E6%B3%A8%E7%B6%B2%E9%96%8B%E6%88%B6\"></span><span class=\"tadv-color\" style=\"color: #0693e3;\"><strong>八、球半\\兩球盤：正規投注網開戶</strong></span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>上下盤各50%，小球多於大球，本人對此盤很少關注。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E4%B9%9D%E3%80%81%E9%97%9C%E6%96%BC%E7%9B%A4%E5%8F%A3%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%8A%E5%8B%95%EF%BC%9A%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%8F%E6%8A%95%E6%B3%A8%E7%B6%B2%E9%96%8B%E6%88%B6\"></span><span class=\"tadv-color\" style=\"color: #0693e3;\"><strong>九、關於盤口的變動：正規投注網開戶</strong></span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>盤口的變動是莊家迷惑投資者的一種方式，用來打消投注者的信心，尤其是臨場變盤請大家注意！！！本人只對一種變盤有信心——先升後降，個人統計這樣的變盤上盤有80%的機會。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E5%8D%81%E3%80%81%E5%82%99%E8%A8%BB%EF%BC%9A%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%8F%E6%8A%95%E6%B3%A8%E7%B6%B2%E9%96%8B%E6%88%B6%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E7%9B%A4%E5%8F%A3%E5%9D%87%E7%82%BA%E5%88%9D%E7%9B%A4%E3%80%82\"></span><span class=\"tadv-color\" style=\"color: #0693e3;\"><strong>十、備註：正規投注網開戶以上盤口均為初盤。</strong></span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<!--codes_iframe--><!--/codes_iframe-->			</div>\r\n\r\n						</article>\r\n</div>', '2022-05-25 06:16:32'),
(50, 111, '博球心理學 ', '博球十一點專業建議', NULL, 1, 0, '<div class=\"product\">\r\n<article id=\"post-1709\" class=\"post-1709 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail  category-43 single-post-content \">\r\n						<div class=\"post-header post-tp-1-header\">\r\n									<h1 class=\"single-post-title\">\r\n						<span class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">博球心理學 享受遊戲樂趣</span></h1>\r\n										<div class=\"post-meta-wrap clearfix\">\r\n						<div class=\"term-badges \"><span class=\"term-badge term-43\">玩運彩技巧教學</span></div>					</div>\r\n									<div class=\"single-featured\">\r\n									</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n						<div class=\"entry-content clearfix single-post-content\">\r\n				<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_22 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-light-blue\">\r\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\r\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">內容目錄</p>\r\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: inline;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"></i></a></span></div>\r\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"#%E5%8D%9A%E7%90%83%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%80%E9%BB%9E%E5%B0%88%E6%A5%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0\" title=\"博球十一點專業建議\">博球十一點專業建議</a></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-102d69ee-ee3c-4d17-8d93-c5d4ab05be10\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>在<strong>博弈</strong>學理的探討與對沖中，深深感到，在主流國際博彩界，關於<strong><em>賠率體系、資金控制、風險機制</em></strong>等主要方面已經相當成熟，並逐步形成了基本定型的運作框架，同時，如何控制過度博彩行為的研究已經相對而言成為一門顯學。很多歐洲的博彩公司均取得共識：取得在經營銷售擴張與控制過度博彩行為上的平衡，對於博彩公司與玩家來說，都是重要的和基本的。香港賽馬會足球博彩在這方面尤其著力。對於廣大玩家而言，也許在一 個歐洲同行給我們的電子郵件裡提到的以下十一點意見中，可以找到端正博球者心理的有益的方法：</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img width=\"70%\" class=\"wp-image-1732 b-loaded\" alt=\"足球博彩心得\" srcset=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/_aol4_fdq3m-240x300.jpg 240w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/_aol4_fdq3m-768x960.jpg 768w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/_aol4_fdq3m-819x1024.jpg 819w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/_aol4_fdq3m.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 240px) 100vw, 240px\" src=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/_aol4_fdq3m-240x300.jpg\">\r\n<figcaption>博球心理學</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-5f40faa2-9ef3-4b29-abd9-e5c00cd4eb43\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E5%8D%9A%E7%90%83%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%80%E9%BB%9E%E5%B0%88%E6%A5%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0\"></span><strong>博球十一點專業建議</strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-f7d098d8-46e1-4c81-b4f7-fb87e7b596de\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p class=\"has-background has-luminous-vivid-amber-background-color\">1，一定要有節制的博彩，定義其為一種特殊的娛樂活動，充分享受遊戲樂趣，但不要超出自身的經濟承受能力；</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\">2，看不懂，看不准，沒有把握時不下注，沒有認識的賽事是危險的，足球是充滿技術含量與智慧含量的，以運氣而論是無法取得持續性成功的；千萬不能有僥倖心理，因為僥倖是風險激增的根源；</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p class=\"has-background has-luminous-vivid-amber-background-color\">3，適可而止，見好就收，得心應手的時候，切忌得意忘形，連戰連敗的時候，切忌心浮氣躁，因為貪婪和恐懼是博球之大忌；</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\">4，果斷而不衝動，永遠計畫好你的資金，保存最大的實力</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p class=\"has-background has-luminous-vivid-amber-background-color\">5，分配好你的籌碼，即不要孤注一擲，也不要平均安排，而是有層次有輕重的投注；</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\">6，制定長期的投資計畫，常贏永遠比大賺難得，但也更重要，每次設立一個止損數，以免擴大損失面，因為重挫一次要很長時間才能恢復，既費時間又費力氣，更易搞壞心態；</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p class=\"has-background has-luminous-vivid-amber-background-color\">7，一個精明的足球投資者，應該把重點投入在標準盤和獨贏盤上，其他高賠率高誘惑的玩法：例如波膽、過關等作為輔助。博彩公司在這些玩法上佔有更為突出的優勢；</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\">8，做一個善於學習的玩家，賽後總結經驗規律，賽前做足功課。這種功課並非是研究各類新聞，而是充分比較歐洲盤與亞洲盤，及時記錄每次盤路變化，一段時間下來，你會有自己的體會和認知；</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p class=\"has-background has-luminous-vivid-amber-background-color\">9，不盲從大流，不聽別人的意見，只相信自己的分析與感覺，當受注出現一邊倒時，你最好冷靜的觀察，要不在對立面，最好是堅決放棄；</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\" style=\"text-align: left;\">10，不通盤研究全部的比賽，尤其是週末的球賽，雖然每場比賽本質上是一樣的。博彩公司正儘量用越來越多的賽事來分散投注量，聰明的玩家應該儘量選擇自己熟悉的聯賽長期研究；</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p class=\"has-background has-luminous-vivid-amber-background-color\">11，極端重視歐洲賠率，學會看盤與比較賠率。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-undefined\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h4>博球做為人認識、選擇、判斷、抗干擾、決定等一系列心理活動的體現，牽涉到潛意識、知識的自主吸納與銳化等多方面的概念。如果能正視以上11點，你將在策略上取得真正的主動。</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<!--codes_iframe--><!--/codes_iframe-->			</div>\r\n\r\n						</article>\r\n</div>', '2022-05-25 06:16:32'),
(51, 116, '博球名詞解釋', '讓球盤、獨贏、走盤', NULL, 1, 0, '<div class=\"product\">\r\n<article id=\"post-943\" class=\"post-943 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail  category-43 single-post-content \">\r\n						<div class=\"post-header post-tp-1-header\">\r\n									<h1 class=\"single-post-title\">\r\n						<span class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">博球名詞解釋：讓球盤、獨贏、走盤</span></h1>\r\n										<div class=\"post-meta-wrap clearfix\">\r\n						<div class=\"term-badges \"><span class=\"term-badge term-43\">玩運彩技巧教學</span></div>					</div>\r\n									<div class=\"single-featured\">\r\n									</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n						<div class=\"entry-content clearfix single-post-content\">\r\n				<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_22 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-light-blue\">\r\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\r\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">內容目錄</p>\r\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: inline;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"></i></a></span></div>\r\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"#%E5%90%8D%E8%A9%9E%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8B\" title=\"名詞解釋\">名詞解釋</a><ul class=\"ez-toc-list-level-3\"><li class=\"ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"#%E8%AE%93%E7%90%83%E7%9B%A4%E7%A8%AE%E9%A1%9E\" title=\"讓球盤種類\">讓球盤種類</a></li></ul></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\">\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_944\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-944\" style=\"width: 70%\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img class=\"wp-image-944 size-large b-loaded\" alt=\"最簡單的歐賠思路\" width=\"1024\" height=\"573\" srcset=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/cuhqcfp3by4-1024x573.jpg 1024w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/cuhqcfp3by4-300x168.jpg 300w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/cuhqcfp3by4-768x430.jpg 768w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/cuhqcfp3by4.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/cuhqcfp3by4-1024x573.jpg\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-944\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">最簡單的歐賠思路</figcaption></figure>\r\n<figcaption><strong>博球名詞解釋：讓球盤、獨贏、走盤</strong></figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-b55398ec-0002-478d-97cd-249e066d0b66\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E5%90%8D%E8%A9%9E%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8B\"></span>名詞解釋<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-f840b32e-6e15-482c-9cf8-65317594da43\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>讓球盤又叫獨贏，可以理解為在指定的比賽中投注勝出的球隊。如果賽果結合讓球為平局，那麽玩家的投注金額將全數退回，此俗稱走盤。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>一般來說，讓球盤由三個部分組成，參加比賽的兩支球隊、讓球數(俗稱盤口，如上例中半球/一球)及貼水，即比賽結果出來以後，博彩者的獲取彩金的系數。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>這裡要和玩家說明一下，亞洲博彩公司讓球盤在一般情況下有兩種貼水，一種是以澳門博彩公司為代表的、上下盤貼水總和為1.85，另外一種俗稱印尼盤，上下盤貼水總和為1.90。同時，貼水又根據數額的高低分為低水、平水、高水。另外，參加比賽的兩支球隊俗稱為上盤、下盤。而其中讓球的一方為上盤。如果盤口為平手，則貼水低的一方為上盤。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-442d8e60-8ec7-4185-8cb1-6671a845e34a\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E8%AE%93%E7%90%83%E7%9B%A4%E7%A8%AE%E9%A1%9E\"></span>讓球盤種類<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-365a6eb0-f8a0-4380-89c7-0bb2fbfd4a4b\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>讓球盤又包括單票和套票兩種。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>單票指的是一場比賽中一支球隊開出一個讓球盤，例如：國際米蘭半球羅馬，則投注者的金額將全部投注在該讓球盤的盤口上。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>套票指的是一場比賽中一支球隊開出兩個讓球盤，例如：雷吉納半球/一球尤文圖斯。那麼，投注者的金額將平均分成兩份，即一半投注在雷吉納讓半球的盤口上，另一半則投注在雷吉納讓一球的盤口上。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<!--codes_iframe--><!--/codes_iframe-->			</div>\r\n\r\n						</article>\r\n</div>', '2022-05-25 06:47:05');
INSERT INTO `product` (`p_id`, `classid`, `p_name`, `p_intro`, `p_price`, `p_open`, `p_cart`, `p_content`, `p_date`) VALUES
(52, 116, '國外博球形式', '介紹幾種國外常見的博球形式', NULL, 1, 0, '<div class=\"product\">\r\n<article id=\"post-3768\" class=\"post-3768 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail  category-43 single-post-content \">\r\n						<div class=\"post-header post-tp-1-header\">\r\n									<h1 class=\"single-post-title\">\r\n						<span class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">介紹幾種國外常見的博球形式</span></h1>\r\n										<div class=\"post-meta-wrap clearfix\">\r\n						<div class=\"term-badges \"><span class=\"term-badge term-43\">玩運彩技巧教學</span></div>					</div>\r\n									<div class=\"single-featured\">\r\n									</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n						<div class=\"entry-content clearfix single-post-content\">\r\n				<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_22 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-light-blue\">\r\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\r\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">內容目錄</p>\r\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: inline;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"></i></a></span></div>\r\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"#%E4%BB%8B%E7%B4%B9%E5%B9%BE%E7%A8%AE%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%96%E5%B8%B8%E8%A6%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E7%90%83%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F\" title=\"介紹幾種國外常見的博球形式\">介紹幾種國外常見的博球形式</a><ul class=\"ez-toc-list-level-3\"><li class=\"ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"#1%E3%80%81%E3%80%8C%E5%B0%BC%E6%A1%91%E4%B8%89%E6%AE%B5%E3%80%8D%E8%B3%BDNassau\" title=\"1、「尼桑三段」賽(Nassau)\">1、「尼桑三段」賽(Nassau)</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"#2%E3%80%81%E3%80%8C%E5%89%9D%E7%9A%AE%E3%80%8D%E8%B3%BDSkins\" title=\"2、「剝皮」賽(Skins)\">2、「剝皮」賽(Skins)</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"#3%E3%80%81%E3%80%8C%E4%BA%BA%E7%8B%BC%E3%80%8D%E9%85%8D%E5%B0%8D%E8%B3%BDWolf\" title=\"3、「人狼」配對賽(Wolf)\">3、「人狼」配對賽(Wolf)</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"#4%E3%80%81%E9%BB%9E%E6%95%B8%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BDPoints\" title=\"4、點數比賽(Points)\">4、點數比賽(Points)</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"#5%E3%80%81%E3%80%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E8%B7%9D%E9%9B%A2%E3%80%8D%E8%B3%BDDollar_a_Yard\" title=\"5、「美元距離」賽(Dollar a Yard)\">5、「美元距離」賽(Dollar a Yard)</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"#6%E3%80%81%E3%80%8C%E7%B2%89%E7%B4%85%E5%A5%B3%E9%83%8E%E3%80%8D%E8%B3%BDPink_Lady\" title=\"6、「粉紅女郎」賽(Pink Lady)\">6、「粉紅女郎」賽(Pink Lady)</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"#7%E3%80%81%E3%80%8C%E9%99%84%E5%8A%A0%E8%B3%AD%E6%B3%A8%E3%80%8D%E8%B3%BDJunk_or_Side_Cheese\" title=\"7、「附加賭注」賽(Junk or Side Cheese)\">7、「附加賭注」賽(Junk or Side Cheese)</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"#8%E3%80%81%E3%80%8C%E6%8A%BC%E8%B1%AC%E6%A5%B5%E7%AB%AF%E3%80%8D%E8%B3%BDHog_Press\" title=\"8、「押豬極端」賽(Hog Press)\">8、「押豬極端」賽(Hog Press)</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"#9%E3%80%81%E3%80%8C%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%8F%E5%A8%81%E5%A4%B7%E3%80%8D%E8%B3%BDThe_Big_Hawaiian\" title=\"9、「大夏威夷」賽(The Big Hawaiian)\">9、「大夏威夷」賽(The Big Hawaiian)</a></li></ul></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-338c0c2f-d3e5-40fa-8b83-1dbcc8fc3ba8\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E4%BB%8B%E7%B4%B9%E5%B9%BE%E7%A8%AE%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%96%E5%B8%B8%E8%A6%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E7%90%83%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F\"></span><strong>介紹幾種國外常見的博球形式</strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img width=\"70%\" class=\"wp-image-2331 b-loaded\" alt=\"介紹幾種國外常見的博球形式\" srcset=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/93bf1fa8d9bbe541fd1ed6a4779db1622eb6853a-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/93bf1fa8d9bbe541fd1ed6a4779db1622eb6853a-300x169.jpg 300w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/93bf1fa8d9bbe541fd1ed6a4779db1622eb6853a-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/93bf1fa8d9bbe541fd1ed6a4779db1622eb6853a.jpg 1199w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/93bf1fa8d9bbe541fd1ed6a4779db1622eb6853a-1024x576.jpg\">\r\n<figcaption>介紹幾種國外常見的博球形式</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-3c8889ae-f9f7-4d73-bc37-5516dd01419d\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>也許你已經厭倦了現有的遊戲方式，那就再介紹幾種比較流行的DB方式，僅僅是作為一個遊戲，不要太認真。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1%E3%80%81%E3%80%8C%E5%B0%BC%E6%A1%91%E4%B8%89%E6%AE%B5%E3%80%8D%E8%B3%BDNassau\"></span>1、「尼桑三段」賽(Nassau)<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>這是一種發展比較成熟的、比較流行的比賽形式。 Nassau是一種最佳球比洞賽，兩人為一隊，這是隊與隊之間的較量，每一隊只需要一個最好成績與另一對較量，這樣的好處是如果隊裡有一個人失誤也沒有關系，還有另一個人的成績可以與別人抗衡。 Nassau是將整個比賽分為三段，前9、後9以及整個18洞。 賭資有自己決定，例如2-2-4的方式，就是前9後9都是押2美元，18洞押4美元，如果全部都贏了就贏得了8美元。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2%E3%80%81%E3%80%8C%E5%89%9D%E7%9A%AE%E3%80%8D%E8%B3%BDSkins\"></span>2、「剝皮」賽(Skins)<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>請不要被這個名字嚇住了，這確實是一個有點暴力的名字，雖然遊戲並沒有這麼暴力，但如果掌握了遊戲的規則，這種遊戲的殘忍程度有時有目共睹的。 所謂Skins就是將球洞看做是一張一張的skin，每一張皮可以值一定的賭資，假定一張皮是1美元，誰贏了第一個洞誰就獲得一美元，如果第一個洞平局那麼這張皮就累積到下一個洞，第二個洞就值兩張皮。 這樣進行下去很有可能在很久都是平局的情況下突然發揮出色，在一個洞將所有的皮都收入囊中。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3%E3%80%81%E3%80%8C%E4%BA%BA%E7%8B%BC%E3%80%8D%E9%85%8D%E5%B0%8D%E8%B3%BDWolf\"></span>3、「人狼」配對賽(Wolf)<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>每一個洞有一個人被事先指定為「狼」，這頭「狼」一般是最後一個發球，他有權利在看完其他三個人或者根本不看的情況下選擇一個認為自己的隊友，對抗剩下的兩個人。 如果這頭「狼」有十足的自信，也可以是選擇以一敵三，當然這種情況下得分將翻倍。 每洞的勝者將得當相應得分數，最後算出總得分。 這種遊戲的有趣之處是，每個洞的對手和同伴都是不同的人，這樣整場比賽也會增添更多的笑料。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4%E3%80%81%E9%BB%9E%E6%95%B8%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BDPoints\"></span>4、點數比賽(Points)<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>每一個洞都有6點的下注，如果這個洞平分，那麼每個球員都有2點；如果兩個球員平分這個洞，那麼他們一個人得3點；如果三個人的成績都不一樣，成績最好的得4點，第二名得2點，最差的那位就不計。 最後算點數的總數，在這裡每一點都可以下一定的賭金。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5%E3%80%81%E3%80%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E8%B7%9D%E9%9B%A2%E3%80%8D%E8%B3%BDDollar_a_Yard\"></span>5、「美元距離」賽(Dollar a Yard)<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Dollar a Yard的規則相對簡單，如果你想贏得一個400碼長的球洞，你需要拿出400美元作為賭金，當然也有人將每一碼的押注降為一角或是一分，不過也不要小看了這些一分錢，在一個長度為7000碼的球場， 賭金也是價值70美元的。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"6%E3%80%81%E3%80%8C%E7%B2%89%E7%B4%85%E5%A5%B3%E9%83%8E%E3%80%8D%E8%B3%BDPink_Lady\"></span>6、「粉紅女郎」賽(Pink Lady)<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>在Pink Lady中，在前一洞輸掉的人必須使用一個粉紅色的高爾夫球，在每9洞結束時成為 「粉紅女郎」的人還要支付相應的金額給其他的球員。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"7%E3%80%81%E3%80%8C%E9%99%84%E5%8A%A0%E8%B3%AD%E6%B3%A8%E3%80%8D%E8%B3%BDJunk_or_Side_Cheese\"></span>7、「附加賭注」賽(Junk or Side Cheese)<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>每一場比賽出了既定的遊戲方式， 還可以附加各種各樣的小賭注， 除了常見的最近球洞獎(greenie)、沙坑挑戰獎(sandy)和小鳥獎(birdie)之外，還有一些創造性的賭注，例如樹皮獎(barkie)、道路獎( roadie)，即擊中樹枝或是道路、球車到仍能獲得標準杆成績的，都可以加注。 只要你能想到的有趣的東西都可以拿來當作加注的藉口。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"8%E3%80%81%E3%80%8C%E6%8A%BC%E8%B1%AC%E6%A5%B5%E7%AB%AF%E3%80%8D%E8%B3%BDHog_Press\"></span>8、「押豬極端」賽(Hog Press)<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>這是一種專為「極端隊伍」設計的遊戲方式。 已經落後的隊伍都會獲得最後一搏的機會，在最後一洞單方面下注，當然賭資也要高於事先為18洞設好的賭資。 贏得最後一洞的人不僅贏得「豬」，還有隨之而來的榮譽和金錢。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"9%E3%80%81%E3%80%8C%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%8F%E5%A8%81%E5%A4%B7%E3%80%8D%E8%B3%BDThe_Big_Hawaiian\"></span>9、「大夏威夷」賽(The Big Hawaiian)<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>The Big Hawaiian是一種比Hog Press更加極端也更讓人心驚膽跳的最後一搏，在最後一洞如果你選擇這種方式，你要在這個洞上下注比如10美元，如果你的隊伍贏得這一洞，那麼之前的負債就一筆勾銷；如果你們平手， 你就輸掉這10美元；當然如果你輸掉了這一洞，你將給每一個人20美元。 這是一項可以讓一個始終領先17洞的人，在最後一洞輸的分文不剩，這樣的對比也是非常吸引人的。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n			</div>\r\n\r\n						</article>\r\n</div>', '2022-05-25 06:47:05'),
(53, 111, '看盤16項基本功', '博友總結出來的看盤16項基本功', NULL, 1, 0, '<div class=\"product\">\r\n<article id=\"post-1497\" class=\"post-1497 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail  category-43 single-post-content \">\r\n						<div class=\"post-header post-tp-1-header\">\r\n									<h1 class=\"single-post-title\">\r\n						<span class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">博友總結出來的看盤16項基本功</span></h1>\r\n										<div class=\"post-meta-wrap clearfix\">\r\n						<div class=\"term-badges \"><span class=\"term-badge term-43\">玩運彩技巧教學</span></div>					</div>\r\n									<div class=\"single-featured\">\r\n									</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n						<div class=\"entry-content clearfix single-post-content\">\r\n				<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_22 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-light-blue\">\r\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\r\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">內容目錄</p>\r\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: inline;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"></i></a></span></div>\r\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"#%E5%8D%9A%E5%8F%8B%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%90%E5%87%BA%E4%BE%86%E7%9A%84%E7%9C%8B%E7%9B%A416%E9%A0%85%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%8A%9F\" title=\"博友總結出來的看盤16項基本功\">博友總結出來的看盤16項基本功</a></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-d6bb4cb6-35af-4a3b-a7d8-cd9118c11db2\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E5%8D%9A%E5%8F%8B%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%90%E5%87%BA%E4%BE%86%E7%9A%84%E7%9C%8B%E7%9B%A416%E9%A0%85%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%8A%9F\"></span><strong>博友總結出來的看盤16項基本功</strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-6a75c67b-2eff-4ac3-8a59-1f41711440ae\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>1、強強對話，客讓半球勝面高</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>2、平/半 升盤 平手，升水再降盤再升水，下盤球隊不敗</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>3、強對弱：一球盤，受注高鋒前3小時，退半/一盤，上盤過熱，臨場不降水反倒升水，以淺誘上，上盤不利</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>4、當歐賠支持平手的時候，亞盤受注高鋒時強升平盤，上盤不利。舉例：1.025 平手 0.825，受注高鋒的時候，變成0.80 受平/半 1.05</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>5、強隊如果長時間保持半/一80水，上盤難勝</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>6、主隊近期狀態很好，主場遇到相同實力的球隊僅讓平手，上盤不利</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>7、豪門球隊做客，有一種淺誘和深誘的套路，有時候僅讓平/半，而且給出925以上的高水，歐賠方面也僅略支持上盤，這種盤有時候往往打出&nbsp; 的機率還比較大。但是如果讓半球，而且給出925以上的高水，在受注高鋒時候，水位沒有什麼變化，那麼上盤很危險</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>8、強隊做客讓半/一球85以上中低水，澳門Aomen水位變化很亂，一上一下，波動很大，即是受關注的比賽，但是到臨場的時候，水位還這樣上下波 動，直至臨場30分鐘後下盤水位竟然還上升，那麼下盤球隊有望贏盤（考慮標盤和局）</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>9、澳門Aomen在黃金受注時間，從平手盤兩度升盤至半球，上盤絕殺</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>10、歐賠沒有動的情況下，澳門Aomen獨自調高上盤球隊主勝，水位變動不符合，上盤不利</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>11、主場龍讓客場蟲球隊僅一球，上盤不利</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>12、排名前三甲對陣最後一名或者倒數第二名的時候，盤口低於一球半，是看低上盤的表現</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>13、往績並不占優，主隊球隊強開平/半，上盤有利</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>14、澳門Aomen標盤變動，一般是升盤升水，降盤降水，如果上盤降水，標盤反倒升水，這是很明顯的上盤難出</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>15、歐賠支持一球盤，澳門Aomen僅開半/一球盤，而且是中水開始降到低水，如果結合的是立博1.57體系賠率，上盤必死（超重） 16、歐賠沒有任何變動的情況下，澳門Aomen獨自降盤，赤裸裸顯示對上盤沒信心。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<!--codes_iframe--><!--/codes_iframe-->			</div>\r\n\r\n						</article>\r\n</div>', '2022-05-25 07:45:04'),
(54, 25, '德州撲克技巧教學', '1.高手總結贏牌技巧<br>\r\n2.線上德州撲克室賺錢的原理', NULL, 1, 0, '<div class=\"product\">\r\n<article id=\"post-979\" class=\"post-979 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail  category-47 single-post-content \">\r\n						<div class=\"post-header post-tp-1-header\">\r\n									<h1 class=\"single-post-title\">\r\n						<span class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">1-1.[德州撲克]Texas Hold’em高手總結赢牌技巧一</span></h1>\r\n										<div class=\"post-meta-wrap clearfix\">\r\n						<div class=\"term-badges \"><span class=\"term-badge term-47\">德州撲克技巧教學</span></div>					</div>\r\n									<div class=\"single-featured\">\r\n									</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n						<div class=\"entry-content clearfix single-post-content\">\r\n				<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_22 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-light-blue\">\r\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\r\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">內容目錄</p>\r\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: inline;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"></i></a></span></div>\r\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"#%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%90%E5%BF%83%E8%88%87%E5%BC%B7%E7%89%8C%E6%98%AF%E7%8E%A9%E5%BE%B7%E5%B7%9E%E6%92%B2%E5%85%8B%E8%87%B4%E5%8B%9D%E7%9A%84%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5%E3%80%82\" title=\"位置，耐心與強牌是玩德州撲克致勝的關鍵。\">位置，耐心與強牌是玩德州撲克致勝的關鍵。</a><ul class=\"ez-toc-list-level-3\"><li class=\"ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"#%E7%AA%A9%E7%89%8C\" title=\"窩牌\">窩牌</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"#%E7%9B%B2%E6%B3%A8\" title=\"盲注\">盲注</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"#%E6%87%B8%E7%89%8C\" title=\"懸牌\">懸牌</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"#%E8%BD%89%E7%89%8CThe_Turn\" title=\"轉牌(The Turn)\">轉牌(The Turn)</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"#%E6%B2%B3%E7%89%8CThe_River\" title=\"河牌(The River)&nbsp;\">河牌(The River)&nbsp;</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"#%E8%AA%8D%E7%9C%9F%E8%A7%80%E5%AF%9FReading_The_Board\" title=\"認真觀察(Reading The Board)&nbsp;\">認真觀察(Reading The Board)&nbsp;</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"#%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E5%B0%8D%E6%89%8BPay_Attention\" title=\"注意對手(Pay Attention)&nbsp;\">注意對手(Pay Attention)&nbsp;</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"#%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96\" title=\"其他\">其他</a></li></ul></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\">\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_972\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-972\"  class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img  width=\"70%\" class=\"wp-image-972 size-large b-loaded\" alt=\"[德州撲克]Texas Hold\'em高手總結贏牌技巧一\"  srcset=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/ot-xbatcotq-1024x680.jpg 1024w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/ot-xbatcotq-300x199.jpg 300w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/ot-xbatcotq-768x510.jpg 768w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/ot-xbatcotq-1536x1020.jpg 1536w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/ot-xbatcotq.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/ot-xbatcotq-1024x680.jpg\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-972\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">[德州撲克]Texas Hold’em高手總結贏牌技巧一</figcaption></figure>\r\n<figcaption>[德州撲克]Texas Hold’em高手總結贏牌技巧一</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-07f07870-2075-4b3b-a5a0-64bacc46f66e\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-none\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%90%E5%BF%83%E8%88%87%E5%BC%B7%E7%89%8C%E6%98%AF%E7%8E%A9%E5%BE%B7%E5%B7%9E%E6%92%B2%E5%85%8B%E8%87%B4%E5%8B%9D%E7%9A%84%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5%E3%80%82\"></span>位置，耐心與強牌是玩德州撲克致勝的關鍵。<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>你第一個最重要的決定是當你拿到兩張窩牌以後，確定這兩張窩牌是否值得你下注進入遊戲。德州撲克玩家能犯的最大錯誤就是窩牌很差時也下注。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>玩牌過程中你相對於鈕扣的位置非常重要，在有10個玩家的牌桌上，緊挨大盲注左邊的三個玩家處於前面位置，下面的三個玩家處於中間位置，所有其他的玩家處於後面位置。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-aa23d66a-846b-4e09-94ba-fbf7e9268cce\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E7%AA%A9%E7%89%8C\"></span>窩牌<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-f82d77f6-47c4-4b6a-9e20-562520ac09d4\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>當你處於前位時，你需要非常強的窩牌才可下注，因為你後面的玩家可能加註再加註。因此耐心等待一手好的窩牌然後在適當的位置下注跟注或加註，對於德州撲克玩家來講，非常重要。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>下面是當你處於不同位置拿到不同窩牌時應採取的不同行動</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>如果你的窩牌是 A-A, K-K and A-Ks (s 是指兩張同花牌) ，無論你處於那個位置都要加註</li>\r\n<li>前面位置(In Early position)如果你的窩牌是 A-K, A-Qs, K-Qs, Q-Q J-J, T-T，你跟注而不要加註，任何其他的窩牌全部棄牌</li>\r\n<li>中間位置(In Middle position) 窩牌為A-K, A-Qs, K-Qs, Q-Q J-J, T-T時加註，窩牌為9-9, 8-8, A-Js, A-Ts, Q-Js, A-Q, K-Q時跟注，其他窩牌全棄牌。</li>\r\n<li>後面位置(In Late position )窩牌為A-K, A-Qs, K-Qs, Q-Q J-J, T-T,9-9, 8-8, A-Js, A-Ts, Q-Js, A-Q, K-Q時加註，窩牌為A-Xs, K-Ts, Q-Ts, J-Ts, A-J, A-T&nbsp; X-X時跟注，(X-X指任何小對) 如果前面玩家已經加註或再加註，你應該考慮棄牌</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>許多玩家只要窩牌為兩張同花或一張A加一張小牌，在任何位置他們都會下注，這些窩牌是一個陷阱，長遠來講會讓你輸錢。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-1d35dc9e-9034-448b-ab9c-ddff8f43e8b3\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E7%9B%B2%E6%B3%A8\"></span>盲注<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-d867f6a3-9f9e-44eb-9101-c65c5ec22409\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>一旦你下了盲注，錢不再屬於你。許多玩家為不白白扔掉盲注而玩一些不該玩的窩牌，不值得。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-68f1dfc3-9b4e-4d3f-80f6-866cfa39e486\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E6%87%B8%E7%89%8C\"></span>懸牌<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-297f4162-8f02-4136-9879-73dc751dc91c\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>看了懸牌以後，是否要棄牌，下注或加註是你要做的第二個重要決定，如果你的牌不是很好，這可能是一個最昂貴的決定。因為看了懸牌以後，你牌的強弱已經確定71%了。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>71%是怎麼來的？因為看了懸牌之後，你已經知道了7張牌中的5張牌，即這手牌的5/7 ，相當與71%。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>這時候你已有足夠的信息決定是否玩下去。一般來講，看過懸牌以後，如果你沒有一對最大牌，也沒有同花或順子的可能，如果你窩牌是一對小牌，沒有形成三張同號，這時候你前面的玩家下注或加註，你應該考慮棄牌。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-d03d5fcb-cefb-441d-a9de-19d3df974dee\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E8%BD%89%E7%89%8CThe_Turn\"></span>轉牌(The Turn)<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-97737b6c-a031-445e-a63b-071991a373ca\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>看了轉牌以後，如果你認為你的牌很好，豪不猶豫的加註。如果你前面的玩家加註，而你只有一對大牌，你應該考慮棄牌。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-9b1e1e9c-cbd4-41b3-8e92-eee0a4171e09\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E6%B2%B3%E7%89%8CThe_River\"></span>河牌(The River)&nbsp;<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-33907fa4-4f6c-41da-94de-2470ab0bf483\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>如果你玩法正確，你不需要看河牌就能決定是否下注。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>看了河牌以後，玩家易犯兩個錯誤：</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>明顯會輸的牌也跟注</li>\r\n<li>輕易棄牌。很顯然，輕易棄牌損失更大，因此如果你還有一些贏的機會，不要輕易棄牌</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-6af07d92-f975-46ea-ae2c-cd86bc5c9413\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E8%AA%8D%E7%9C%9F%E8%A7%80%E5%AF%9FReading_The_Board\"></span>認真觀察(Reading The Board)&nbsp;<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-d2e9d7a2-dbcb-4e90-85bb-e1cda87313c7\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>觀察每個玩家的玩牌技巧下注習慣表情非常重要，因為德州撲克用五張共用牌，很多時候可以猜出其他玩家所能組成的最大牌型，從而確定自己是否該下注。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-78dbceaa-1e37-4151-adc4-676a55190d25\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E5%B0%8D%E6%89%8BPay_Attention\"></span>注意對手(Pay Attention)&nbsp;<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-efa7f750-d8df-4282-afbd-27e273b25915\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>注意對手都玩什麼樣的窩牌，對你下注很有幫助，但不要被對手的某些伎倆所欺騙，因此要多觀察多注意。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>如此短的篇幅不可能教會你玩德州撲克的所有技巧。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>但如果你能掌握並靈活運用上面的策略，你已經比80%的玩家水平要高，你在德州撲克牌桌上贏錢的機會已經遠遠超過你玩二十一點或百家樂贏錢的機會。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-d11ac155-b00e-4a0d-8011-d0eb02e1aeb3\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96\"></span>其他<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-17acbd89-23e1-45ad-8e79-d9af4b5deb5f\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>德州撲克賭桌上有許多玩家玩牌為了娛樂，水平很差，也有一些有錢人，不太在乎輸贏，這些人往往亂玩，只要你能找到他們的弱點，一有機會，很容易將他們的錢贏過來，這是德州撲克成為一種非常有利可圖的賭博遊戲的最大原因</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>玩德州撲克，最重要的是要有耐心，如果你耐心不足，最好不要玩這個遊戲。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<!--codes_iframe--><!--/codes_iframe-->			</div>\r\n\r\n						</article><article id=\"post-1192\" class=\"post-1192 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail  category-47 single-post-content \">\r\n						<div class=\"post-header post-tp-1-header\">\r\n									<h1 class=\"single-post-title\">\r\n						<span class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">1-2.[德州撲克]Texas Hold’em高手總結贏牌技巧二</span></h1>\r\n										<div class=\"post-meta-wrap clearfix\">\r\n						<div class=\"term-badges \"><span class=\"term-badge term-47\">德州撲克技巧教學</span></div>					</div>\r\n									<div class=\"single-featured\">\r\n									</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n						<div class=\"entry-content clearfix single-post-content\">\r\n				<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_22 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-light-blue\">\r\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\r\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">內容目錄</p>\r\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: inline;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"></i></a></span></div>\r\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\" title=\"前言\">前言</a><ul class=\"ez-toc-list-level-3\"><li class=\"ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"#%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E7%8E%87%E8%A1%93%E8%AA%9E\" title=\"常用的概率術語\">常用的概率術語</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"#%E8%88%89%E4%BE%8B\" title=\"舉例\">舉例</a></li></ul></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img width=\"70%\" class=\"wp-image-1194 b-loaded\" alt=\"[德州撲克]Texas Hold\'em高手總結贏牌技巧二\" srcset=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/pvivpygm16o-1024x680.jpg 1024w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/pvivpygm16o-300x199.jpg 300w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/pvivpygm16o-768x510.jpg 768w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/pvivpygm16o-1536x1020.jpg 1536w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/pvivpygm16o.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/pvivpygm16o-1024x680.jpg\">\r\n<figcaption>[德州撲克]Texas Hold’em高手總結贏牌技巧二</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-a296ddbf-ad36-4b90-85cf-680240215a28\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\"></span>前言<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-5d0f66da-2cd3-46c5-9587-24f6f627d706\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>玩德州撲克Texas Hold’em過程中，一副牌形成的可能性有多大，對你下一步採取什麼樣的行動至關重要。一副牌形成的可能性有多大可以用成牌概率來計算。形成同花或順子的機會有多大，拿到一張大牌的可能性有多少，當你手中握有一對時，懸牌形成三張同號的百分比為幾，這些概率學上的知識對於德州撲克Texas Hold’em一輪牌的輸贏非常關鍵，這些概率的計算決定你下一步是下注，跟注，加註還是棄牌。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-104d9256-b256-4b1c-9ea2-544676743621\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E7%8E%87%E8%A1%93%E8%AA%9E\"></span>常用的概率術語<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-d74b3daa-54b7-46cf-b490-e8f7d7bd8a82\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figcaption>常用的概率術語</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-8950c6b4-fb94-4830-a870-4a7164fc9083\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E8%88%89%E4%BE%8B\"></span>舉例<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-7b3ad7b9-ee0f-4cad-b355-a4596068ef2b\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>轉牌翻開以後，你有四張紅桃，你完成紅桃同花牌型概率為9比47，大約為5分之1，你相信同花會贏這輪牌，而這時的總賭注為$200，你只要再跟注$20就可以看到河牌，總注概率為20比200，即為十分之一，這就是說，如果出現5次這種情況，你贏1次輸4次，你贏一次的錢為$200，而你輸4次的錢總數為$80，你1次贏錢的總數遠大於你4次輸錢的總數，因此這種情況下你一定要跟牌而不是棄牌。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>反過來，如果這時的總賭注為$60，而你要跟注$20才可以看到河牌，總注概率為20比60，即為3分之1，這就是說，如果出現5次這種情況，你贏1次輸4次，你贏一次的錢為$60，而你輸4次的錢總數為$80，你一次贏錢的總數小於你4次輸錢的總數，因此這種情況下你一定要棄牌而不是跟牌。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>玩牌過程中，最常用到的是補牌總數與總注概率，如何計算各種輸贏概率，以後會陸續介紹。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<!--codes_iframe--><!--/codes_iframe-->			</div>\r\n\r\n						</article><article id=\"post-1718\" class=\"post-1718 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail  category-47 single-post-content \">\r\n						<div class=\"post-header post-tp-1-header\">\r\n									<h1 class=\"single-post-title\">\r\n						<span class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">2.線上德州撲克室賺錢的原理</span></h1>\r\n										<div class=\"post-meta-wrap clearfix\">\r\n						<div class=\"term-badges \"><span class=\"term-badge term-47\">德州撲克技巧教學</span></div>					</div>\r\n									<div class=\"single-featured\">\r\n									</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n						<div class=\"entry-content clearfix single-post-content\">\r\n				<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_22 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-light-blue\">\r\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\r\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">內容目錄</p>\r\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: inline;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"></i></a></span></div>\r\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"#%E7%B7%9A%E4%B8%8A%E5%BE%B7%E5%B7%9E%E6%92%B2%E5%85%8B%E6%80%8E%E9%BA%BC%E8%B3%BA%E9%8C%A2%EF%BC%9F\" title=\"線上德州撲克怎麼賺錢？\">線上德州撲克怎麼賺錢？</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"#%E7%8E%A9poker%EF%BC%8C%E8%B3%BA%E9%8C%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%892%E7%A8%AE%EF%BC%9A\" title=\"玩poker，賺錢的方式只有2種：&nbsp;\">玩poker，賺錢的方式只有2種：&nbsp;</a><ul class=\"ez-toc-list-level-3\"><li class=\"ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"#1%E6%92%B2%E5%85%8B%E7%89%8C%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E6%B7%B7%E7%B4%85%E5%88%A9\" title=\"1.撲克牌遊戲混紅利\">1.撲克牌遊戲混紅利</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"#2%E6%92%B2%E5%85%8B%E7%89%8C%E7%AE%97%E7%89%8C%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E3%80%81%E7%B6%93%E9%A9%97%E5%92%8C%E9%81%8B%E6%B0%A3\" title=\"2.撲克牌算牌技術、經驗和運氣\">2.撲克牌算牌技術、經驗和運氣</a></li></ul></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-4956 size-large b-loaded\" alt=\"百家樂贏到笑！微笑心法秘訣大公開\" width=\"70%\" srcset=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/百家樂贏到笑！微笑心法秘訣大公開-1024x676.jpg 1024w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/百家樂贏到笑！微笑心法秘訣大公開-300x198.jpg 300w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/百家樂贏到笑！微笑心法秘訣大公開-768x507.jpg 768w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/百家樂贏到笑！微笑心法秘訣大公開.jpg 1324w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/百家樂贏到笑！微笑心法秘訣大公開-1024x676.jpg\">\r\n<figcaption>線上德州撲克賺錢方法</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-0cc22c36-1a2d-45e3-8e19-af16fb8519dd\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E7%B7%9A%E4%B8%8A%E5%BE%B7%E5%B7%9E%E6%92%B2%E5%85%8B%E6%80%8E%E9%BA%BC%E8%B3%BA%E9%8C%A2%EF%BC%9F\"></span>線上德州撲克怎麼賺錢？<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-16e54ae3-90d5-44af-90f7-cdc1676a4d1a\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>線上德州撲克texas holdem是目前世界上最流行的撲克遊戲.起源於北美,現在每年有世界撲克大獎賽WSOP和撲克錦標賽,隨著撲克比賽的開展,電視轉播的介入 ,撲克運動獲的空前的發展.撲克比賽越來越多,參與的人也越來越多,比賽獎金也越來越高.2003年WSOP決賽的第一名獎金高達$250萬。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>線上德州撲克是game的一種，但最大的不同是：你的對手是同你一樣的人,而其他game你對付的是對賭場有利的概率。 撲克是真正可以通過技巧和智慧贏錢的運動,你的對手是其他和你一樣的人，有精明有笨蛋但都會犯錯誤的普通人．德州撲克賭桌上有許多玩家玩牌為了娛樂，水準很差，也有一些有錢人，不太在乎輸贏，這些人往往亂玩，只要你肯學習肯練習,你可以通過網路贏取你的財富。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-7ce1242c-8a44-4da1-ae50-34045c7c2e28\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E7%8E%A9poker%EF%BC%8C%E8%B3%BA%E9%8C%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%892%E7%A8%AE%EF%BC%9A\"></span>玩poker，賺錢的方式只有2種：&nbsp;<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-0c82e6eb-9b69-433f-9f67-b52c6a095e61\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1%E6%92%B2%E5%85%8B%E7%89%8C%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E6%B7%B7%E7%B4%85%E5%88%A9\"></span>1.撲克牌遊戲混紅利<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>混紅利，達到手數或倍數要求，以紅利為根本目的，這基本算poker盈利的初級階段: 網上撲克室成百上千家，競爭很激烈。絕大多數線上撲克室為了吸引客戶，對於新玩家都會有優惠，一般是首次存款送20~100%的紅利，比如你 存100美元，賭場再送你20美元。當然線上撲克室也不傻，你不能馬上把這20美元提走，必須在線上撲克室玩，累計完成一定數目的手數才能提款， 一般是10倍的紅利左右。比如賭場送你20美元，就要求你完成200手的時候才能提款。我們的目標就是儘快達到200手，同時最大程度的保存20美元的紅利。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2%E6%92%B2%E5%85%8B%E7%89%8C%E7%AE%97%E7%89%8C%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E3%80%81%E7%B6%93%E9%A9%97%E5%92%8C%E9%81%8B%E6%B0%A3\"></span>2.撲克牌算牌技術、經驗和運氣<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>贏刀刀。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>這個對技術、經驗，心理素質、資本都要求較高，當渡過混紅利階段，有了一定資金技術經驗積累後，可以考慮這種方式或者繼續堅持混紅利的方式。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--codes_iframe--><!--/codes_iframe-->			</div>\r\n\r\n						</article>\r\n</div>', '2022-05-25 08:01:05'),
(55, 25, '21點技巧教學', '1.一副牌的高級21點算牌法<br>\r\n2.21點的基本策略卡', NULL, 1, 0, '<div class=\"product\">\r\n<article id=\"post-1607\" class=\"post-1607 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail  category-45 single-post-content \">\r\n						<div class=\"post-header post-tp-1-header\">\r\n									<h1 class=\"single-post-title\">\r\n						<span class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">1.一副牌的高級21點算牌法</span></h1>\r\n										<div class=\"post-meta-wrap clearfix\">\r\n						<div class=\"term-badges \"><span class=\"term-badge term-45\">21點技巧教學</span></div>					</div>\r\n									<div class=\"single-featured\">\r\n									</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n						<div class=\"entry-content clearfix single-post-content\">\r\n				<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_22 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-light-blue\">\r\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\r\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">內容目錄</p>\r\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: inline;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"></i></a></span></div>\r\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"#21%E9%BB%9E%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7\" title=\"21點技巧\">21點技巧</a><ul class=\"ez-toc-list-level-3\"><li class=\"ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"#%E4%B8%80%E5%89%AF%E7%89%8C%E7%9A%8421%E9%BB%9E%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%EF%BC%8C%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%B6%E4%BD%94010%E7%9A%84%E5%84%AA%E5%8B%A2%EF%BC%81\" title=\"一副牌的21點遊戲，玩家佔0.10%的優勢！\">一副牌的21點遊戲，玩家佔0.10%的優勢！</a></li></ul></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"#21%E9%BB%9E%E7%AE%97%E7%89%8C%E6%B3%95\" title=\"21點算牌法\">21點算牌法</a><ul class=\"ez-toc-list-level-3\"><li class=\"ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"#%E4%B8%8B%E9%9D%A2%E9%80%99%E7%A8%AE%E7%AE%97%E7%89%8C%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E8%88%87%E4%B8%8B%E6%B3%A8%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7%E9%81%A9%E5%90%88%E5%8F%AA%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%80%E5%89%AF%E7%89%8C%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8C%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%80%E9%BB%9E%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2\" title=\"下面這種算牌方法與下注技巧適合只用一副牌的二十一點遊戲\">下面這種算牌方法與下注技巧適合只用一副牌的二十一點遊戲</a></li></ul></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-4983 size-large b-loaded\" alt=\"在澳門玩21點的心路歷程\" width=\"70%\" srcset=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/19624-1200x1200-1-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/19624-1200x1200-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/19624-1200x1200-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/19624-1200x1200-1-768x768.jpg 768w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/19624-1200x1200-1.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/19624-1200x1200-1-1024x1024.jpg\"><br>\r\n<figcaption>一副牌的高級21點算牌法</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-e743f03e-2363-4ef8-a9c7-7f32ced15bc7\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"21%E9%BB%9E%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7\"></span>21點技巧<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-2b973100-304f-44ec-a7df-942875df1580\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E4%B8%80%E5%89%AF%E7%89%8C%E7%9A%8421%E9%BB%9E%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%EF%BC%8C%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%B6%E4%BD%94010%E7%9A%84%E5%84%AA%E5%8B%A2%EF%BC%81\"></span>一副牌的21點遊戲，玩家佔0.10%的優勢！<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>別小看這0.10%，這是唯一玩家佔優勢的娛樂場遊戲。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>正因為如此，基本上沒有什麼娛樂場敢於提供，再加上算牌，莊家慘了！</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-74084944-8e3b-45b4-989b-e7e6fceadc04\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"21%E9%BB%9E%E7%AE%97%E7%89%8C%E6%B3%95\"></span>21點算牌法<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-ba6ff781-a4b2-4328-98b2-4696554b6d03\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E4%B8%8B%E9%9D%A2%E9%80%99%E7%A8%AE%E7%AE%97%E7%89%8C%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E8%88%87%E4%B8%8B%E6%B3%A8%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7%E9%81%A9%E5%90%88%E5%8F%AA%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%80%E5%89%AF%E7%89%8C%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8C%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%80%E9%BB%9E%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2\"></span>下面這種算牌方法與下注技巧<strong>適合只用一副牌的二十一點遊戲</strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>設定初始算牌總值為4</li>\r\n<li>10, J, Q, K 的賦予值為 -2</li>\r\n<li>所有其它牌的賦予值為 +1</li>\r\n<li>開始發牌後按照發出牌所賦予的值進行加減計算出牌總值以確定如何下注，當出牌總值為負數時，下注要小，當出牌總值為正數時，下注要大</li>\r\n<li>只有出牌總值為正數時買保險</li>\r\n<li>玩牌過程中按照21點基本策略要牌或不要牌</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--codes_iframe--><!--/codes_iframe-->			</div>\r\n\r\n						</article><article id=\"post-1259\" class=\"post-1259 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail  category-45 single-post-content \">\r\n						<div class=\"post-header post-tp-1-header\">\r\n									<h1 class=\"single-post-title\">\r\n						<span class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">2. 21點的基本策略卡</span></h1>\r\n										<div class=\"post-meta-wrap clearfix\">\r\n						<div class=\"term-badges \"><span class=\"term-badge term-45\">21點技巧教學</span></div>					</div>\r\n									<div class=\"single-featured\">\r\n									</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n						<div class=\"entry-content clearfix single-post-content\">\r\n				<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_22 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-light-blue\">\r\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\r\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">內容目錄</p>\r\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: inline;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"></i></a></span></div>\r\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5\" title=\"基本策略:\">基本策略:</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"#%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E4%BD%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%88%B0A%E7%89%8C\" title=\"如果你拿到A牌:\">如果你拿到A牌:</a><ul class=\"ez-toc-list-level-3\"><li class=\"ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"#%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E6%99%82%E5%80%99%E5%88%86%E7%89%8C\" title=\"什麼時候分牌:\">什麼時候分牌:</a></li></ul></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img width=\"70%\"  class=\"wp-image-1263 b-loaded\" alt=\"21點的基本策略卡 \" srcset=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/賭場百家樂vs真人百家樂.jpg 999w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/賭場百家樂vs真人百家樂-300x246.jpg 300w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/賭場百家樂vs真人百家樂-768x630.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 999px) 100vw, 999px\" src=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/賭場百家樂vs真人百家樂.jpg\">\r\n<figcaption>21點的基本策略卡</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-e96f2fec-aee1-4f5d-a5d9-2ea311ac938f\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5\"></span><strong>基本策略</strong><strong>:</strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-885fc66b-01eb-42da-8056-4963d614e4ec\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img width=\"70%\"  class=\"wp-image-1260\" data-src=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/image-27.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/image-27.png 482w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/image-27-300x218.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 482px) 100vw, 482px\">\r\n<figcaption><strong>基本策略</strong></figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-df4ddb60-ea15-4531-8c13-645689eaf7a1\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E4%BD%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%88%B0A%E7%89%8C\"></span><strong>如果你拿到</strong><strong>A</strong><strong>牌</strong><strong>:</strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-071ca5b8-b008-46b3-9fa1-91763ab64282\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img width=\"70%\"  class=\"wp-image-1261\" data-src=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/image-28.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/image-28.png 482w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/image-28-300x179.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 482px) 100vw, 482px\">\r\n<figcaption><strong>如果你拿到A牌</strong></figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-2485868f-74b6-4d26-843b-97061023fc4c\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E6%99%82%E5%80%99%E5%88%86%E7%89%8C\"></span><strong>什麼時候分牌</strong><strong>:</strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-064623d2-ac4b-4f9f-8c21-264b48651f92\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img width=\"70%\"  class=\"wp-image-1262\" data-src=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/image-29.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/image-29.png 482w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/image-29-300x205.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 482px) 100vw, 482px\">\r\n<figcaption><strong>什麼時候分牌</strong></figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<!--codes_iframe--><!--/codes_iframe-->			</div>\r\n\r\n						</article>\r\n</div>', '2022-05-25 08:01:05');
