(56, 25, '百家樂技巧教學2', '1.實戰之止蝕位、止賺位<br>\r\n2.投注方法之三龍合一法', NULL, 1, 0, '<div class=\"product\">\r\n<article id=\"post-610\" class=\"post-610 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail  category-4 single-post-content \">\r\n						<div class=\"post-header post-tp-1-header\">\r\n									<h1 class=\"single-post-title\">\r\n						<span class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">1百家樂實戰之止蝕位、止賺位</span></h1>\r\n										<div class=\"post-meta-wrap clearfix\">\r\n						<div class=\"term-badges \"><span class=\"term-badge term-4\">百家樂技巧教學</span></div>					</div>\r\n									<div class=\"single-featured\">\r\n									</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n						<div class=\"entry-content clearfix single-post-content\">\r\n				<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_22 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-light-blue\">\r\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\r\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">內容目錄</p>\r\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: inline;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"></i></a></span></div>\r\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"#%E7%99%BE%E5%AE%B6%E6%A8%82%E5%AF%A6%E6%88%B0%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%A2%E8%9D%95%E4%BD%8D%E3%80%81%E6%AD%A2%E8%B3%BA%E4%BD%8D\" title=\"百家樂實戰中的止蝕位、止賺位\">百家樂實戰中的止蝕位、止賺位</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"#%E6%AD%A2%E8%9D%95%E4%BD%8D%E3%80%81%E6%AD%A2%E8%B3%BA%E4%BD%8D%E7%9A%84%E8%A8%88%E7%AE%97%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F\" title=\"止蝕位、止賺位的計算方式\">止蝕位、止賺位的計算方式</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"#%E6%80%8E%E9%BA%BC%E6%94%B9%E8%AE%8A%E7%99%BE%E5%AE%B6%E6%A8%82%E7%9A%84%E9%80%99%E5%80%8B%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87%EF%BC%9F\" title=\"怎麼改變百家樂的這個規則？\">怎麼改變百家樂的這個規則？</a></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-0ba8a2eb-585e-4729-b6f4-21594d281d10\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E7%99%BE%E5%AE%B6%E6%A8%82%E5%AF%A6%E6%88%B0%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%A2%E8%9D%95%E4%BD%8D%E3%80%81%E6%AD%A2%E8%B3%BA%E4%BD%8D\"></span>百家樂實戰中的止蝕位、止賺位<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-41ca5a10-d543-44d1-9ba7-504f24b2c775\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E6%AD%A2%E8%9D%95%E4%BD%8D%E3%80%81%E6%AD%A2%E8%B3%BA%E4%BD%8D%E7%9A%84%E8%A8%88%E7%AE%97%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F\"></span>止蝕位、止賺位的計算方式<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>在我未講我個人如何去計算止蝕位，止賺位之前，先問一問大家一個問題，現在有一個賭博遊戲不知大家是否有興趣參與：</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>這賭博遊戲規則如下:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>有一間賭場,裡面有一種賭博遊戲,大家的勝負比率都是50% / 50%</li>\r\n<li>如果你能在這遊戲中勝出一鋪,你就會得到$500 相反你輸了就要從你帶來的本金中扣除$500,每一鋪你都必須要投注,不可停注.</li>\r\n<li>不論你在這賭場贏了多少錢,都不准帶走,只有輸清你帶來的本金才可離開賭場!</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>你是否有興趣參與這賭博遊戲呢? <strong>大家的答案：當然不會參與！</strong></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>但說來也很奇怪！這遊戲，每天都有數不盡的人正在參與，而且..以前我都有份參與！</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&lt;&lt; 相信大家看到這裡 開始明白個中道理了 &gt;&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>要在這同一樣的遊戲當中真正贏錢,首先要改變這遊戲規則,否則我們因為遊戲規則的所限,就算贏了錢都不可帶出賭場! 根據以上的遊戲規則去投注,不輸錢才怪!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img  width=\"70%\" class=\"wp-image-436\" data-src=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/dice-1542458_1280-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/dice-1542458_1280-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/dice-1542458_1280-300x169.jpg 300w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/dice-1542458_1280-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/dice-1542458_1280.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\">\r\n<figcaption>百家樂的止蝕位、止賺位算法</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-de6ea58d-e414-4e6a-948c-56e1635da022\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E6%80%8E%E9%BA%BC%E6%94%B9%E8%AE%8A%E7%99%BE%E5%AE%B6%E6%A8%82%E7%9A%84%E9%80%99%E5%80%8B%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87%EF%BC%9F\"></span>怎麼改變百家樂的這個規則？<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>想贏錢及要改變這不平等的規則只有一個方法,就是需要一個(止蝕位,止賺位),而且還要在進入賭場前,跟賭場簽下一份最新的遊戲規則合約,大家相方都必須要遵守,不得異議.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>(合約) 細節:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>止蝕位 = 當參與者在投注時,輸到一個一早定下的數目,就不准投注,必須要立即離開,當天不得再進入賭場.賭場也不可再接受那參與者的投注.</li>\r\n<li>止賺位 = 當參與者在投注時勝出了,而且已贏到一個一早定下的數目,就不准再投注,必須要立即離開,當天不得再進入賭場, 賭場也不可再接受那參與者的投注. &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>止蝕位,止賺位 的數目 = 由參與者自行設定.</li>\r\n<li>投注,及注碼 = 由參與者自由選擇(可投注 莊 或 閒 ),也可以在某一時段不投注(可以不用每鋪都下注)</li>\r\n<li>離場 = 參與者可隨時離開賭場,不受任何限制.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&lt;&lt; 有了以上的”規則合約”才有機會真正贏錢,當然這所謂”合約”只是假設的,但是非常有道理 &gt;&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>請繼續細看：本金,止蝕位,止賺位的”設計”</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<!--codes_iframe--><!--/codes_iframe-->			</div>\r\n\r\n						</article><article id=\"post-607\" class=\"post-607 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail  category-4 single-post-content \">\r\n						<div class=\"post-header post-tp-1-header\">\r\n									<h1 class=\"single-post-title\">\r\n						<span class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">2.百家樂投注方法之三龍合一法</span></h1>\r\n										<div class=\"post-meta-wrap clearfix\">\r\n						<div class=\"term-badges \"><span class=\"term-badge term-4\">百家樂技巧教學</span></div>					</div>\r\n									<div class=\"single-featured\">\r\n									</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n						<div class=\"entry-content clearfix single-post-content\">\r\n				<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_22 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-light-blue\">\r\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\r\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">內容目錄</p>\r\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: inline;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"></i></a></span></div>\r\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"#%E7%99%BE%E5%AE%B6%E6%A8%82%E4%B8%89%E9%BE%8D%E5%90%88%E4%B8%80%E6%B3%95\" title=\"百家樂三龍合一法\">百家樂三龍合一法</a><ul class=\"ez-toc-list-level-3\"><li class=\"ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"#%E8%B7%B3%E9%BE%8D\" title=\"跳龍\">跳龍</a></li></ul></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"#%E4%B8%89%E9%BE%8D%E5%90%88%E4%B8%80\" title=\"三龍合一\">三龍合一</a></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-06f890d0-5d3a-4279-bb73-b8d6ce11d019\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E7%99%BE%E5%AE%B6%E6%A8%82%E4%B8%89%E9%BE%8D%E5%90%88%E4%B8%80%E6%B3%95\"></span>百家樂三龍合一法<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img width=\"70%\" class=\"wp-image-330 b-loaded\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/card-1298695_1280-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/card-1298695_1280-300x200.jpg 300w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/card-1298695_1280-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/card-1298695_1280-1200x800.jpg 1200w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/card-1298695_1280-600x400.jpg 600w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/card-1298695_1280-675x450.jpg 675w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/card-1298695_1280.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/card-1298695_1280-1024x683.jpg\">\r\n<figcaption>百家樂三龍合一法</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-effc5831-f82d-4a36-a779-7bc961ce736b\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>方法是這：</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>當你看到2個跳時bbbpb這第6口便是切入點，買到$300，中了下一口買$600，中了這時本金共$1200 取回1/3$400；下一口買$800，中了本金共$1600，取回1/2$800，下一口買$800，中了本金共$1600。這時你共下了4口，第一個$100中孖寶，收$400，第二個$100中三關，收$800，第三個$100中四關，收$1600 扣除本錢$300實嬴$2500。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E8%B7%B3%E9%BE%8D\"></span>跳龍<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>第一個階段便告完成，而此時除頭二口單跳外，你共下注四口即巳開了六口，第7口開始由$500起，用嬴谷輸縮樓梯纜下注，直至斷為止……這是跳龍。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-da6692b3-1baa-48e0-b648-832d38386235\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E4%B8%89%E9%BE%8D%E5%90%88%E4%B8%80\"></span>三龍合一<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>如遇長莊/閒也是用這方法和注碼，當你看到bpbpbpbb這時便是切入點買連，如嬴照以上注碼，如輸則停下來。看到有明確的切入點才下注每次止蝕為$1500，止賺為直至斷為止。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>長莊我叫<strong><span class=\"tadv-color\" style=\"color: #cf2e2e;\">紅龍</span></strong>…..</li>\r\n<li>長閒我叫<strong><span class=\"tadv-color\" style=\"color: #0693e3;\">藍龍</span></strong>…..</li>\r\n<li>長跳我叫<strong><span class=\"tadv-color\" style=\"color: #27c088;\">彩龍</span></strong>…..</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>故名三龍合一，另遇上2個2個之局，可祗買第2個便停，以保留實力，等待時機！</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<!--codes_iframe--><!--/codes_iframe-->			</div>\r\n\r\n						</article>\r\n</div>', '2022-05-25 08:01:05'),
(57, 26, '輪盤技巧教學1', '1.玩輪盤的流行下注策略<br>\r\n2.輪盤是可以戰勝的', NULL, 1, 0, '<div class=\"product\">\r\n<article id=\"post-1209\" class=\"post-1209 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail  category-44 single-post-content \">\r\n						<div class=\"post-header post-tp-1-header\">\r\n									<h1 class=\"single-post-title\">\r\n						<span class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">1.玩輪盤的流行下注策略</span></h1>\r\n										<div class=\"post-meta-wrap clearfix\">\r\n						<div class=\"term-badges \"><span class=\"term-badge term-44\">輪盤技巧教學</span></div>					</div>\r\n									<div class=\"single-featured\">\r\n									</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n						<div class=\"entry-content clearfix single-post-content\">\r\n				<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_22 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-light-blue\">\r\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\r\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">內容目錄</p>\r\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: inline;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"></i></a></span></div>\r\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"#%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81%E5%96%AE%E9%9B%99%E6%B3%95\" title=\"一、單雙法\">一、單雙法</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"#%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%81%E4%B8%80%E6%89%93%E6%B3%95\" title=\"二、一打法\">二、一打法</a><ul class=\"ez-toc-list-level-3\"><li class=\"ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"#%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%94%E7%B2%BE%E5%BF%83%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AC%E5%BC%8F\" title=\"常用且精心設計的公式\">常用且精心設計的公式</a></li></ul></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\">\r\n<figcaption>玩輪盤的流行下注策略</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-161e29e8-a0c8-4cdc-9398-d15d8c56333a\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81%E5%96%AE%E9%9B%99%E6%B3%95\"></span><strong>一、單雙法</strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-b8e44328-265d-4756-a419-ae506d272e72\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>用1、2、4、8、16、32、…..的翻倍下注法，只要壓對一次就能賺一刀，具體的壓法是：首先在單雙各壓一刀，只要不出0，就不賺不賠，以後永遠只壓前次所出數字的反面，即前次出雙本次壓單，前次出但本次壓雙。每次從一刀起壓，若不中，下次翻倍，若中了下次重新從一刀起壓。<br><br>按我的經驗，若能有200刀的本，然後堅決以一次贏1刀來操作，一天贏夠10刀就走人，想不贏都難。&nbsp;<br>我的習慣是用1、3、7、15、31、63……的乘2加一下注法，好處是平均每壓一次能賺1刀，缺點是相同賭本下能連續虧的次數少了一次。若以200刀賭本算，贏夠10刀就走人的風險不會比翻倍下注法高，乘2加一下下注壓10次就能賺夠10刀，而翻倍下注法至少要壓20次甚至30次40次。&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-d872e46f-220f-4b2e-8004-0820e9e953f4\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%81%E4%B8%80%E6%89%93%E6%B3%95\"></span><strong>二、一打法</strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-edc6c69a-6381-4cef-bbe7-aa722e0a5389\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>用1、3、9、27、81、……的3倍下注法，只要壓對一次就能賺一刀，具體的壓法是：首先在三個一打下注區各壓一刀，只要不出0，就不賺不賠，以後永遠只壓前次所出一打下注區的另外兩區等額下注，即前次出一區雙本次壓二三區，前次出二區雙本次壓一三區，前次出三區雙本次壓一二區。每次從一刀起壓，若不中，下次翻3倍，若中了下次重新從一刀起壓。&nbsp;<br><br>在drholite賭場一打下注可以從最底1刀壓到最高2500刀，若最低定為25刀則最高能壓2900刀。&nbsp;<br><br>和單雙法一樣贏一次能贏一刀，要想平均一次贏一刀可以用乘3加1下注法，1、4、13、40、121、……..</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>第二種公式(以輪盤賠率為5倍的數字組為押注目標)&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-8fc0953e-c11c-4a26-8ce4-ecd1335ae33f\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%94%E7%B2%BE%E5%BF%83%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AC%E5%BC%8F\"></span>常用且精心設計的公式<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>在統計數字齊備時是獲利較高的方式，完全不藏私，各位仔細看吧。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-b7be1e62-5db7-419e-9fbe-58ecfa8c0c51\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>首先一樣是先押空頭籌碼多次來取得一完整資料，如果是在真正賭場(如站長去麗星游輪)就當然是換了籌碼之後先不要押注，看別人押注來記錄資料。<br>&nbsp;<br>將數字分為6個區域(1～6)、(7～12)、(13～18)、(19～24)、(25～30)、(31～36)&nbsp;<br>完整的記錄。之後就照著下列公式押注。&nbsp;<br><br>舉例： 押注 若中了扣掉投資的淨利 總投資&nbsp;<br>第1次 5美元 25美元 -5美元&nbsp;<br>第2次 6美元 25美元 -11美元&nbsp;<br>第3次 8美元 29美元 -19美元&nbsp;<br>第4次 10美元 31美元 -29美元&nbsp;<br>第5次 12美元 31美元 -41美元&nbsp;<br>第6次 15美元 34美元 -56美元&nbsp;<br>第7次 18美元 34美元 -74美元&nbsp;<br>第8次 22美元 36美元 -96美元&nbsp;<br>第9次 27美元 39美元 -123美元&nbsp;<br>第10次 33美元 42美元 -156美元&nbsp;<br>第11次 40美元 44美元 -196美元&nbsp;<br>第12次 48美元 46美元 -244美元&nbsp;<br>第13次 58美元 45美元 -302美元&nbsp;<br>第14次 70美元 48美元 -372美元&nbsp;<br>第15次 85美元 53美元 -457美元&nbsp;<br><br>正常來說以6/38的機率，連續15次不出現你要的組合約是7.6%&nbsp;<br><br>★意即在15次內有九成三的機率會出現。在你能夠負擔下注金額的情況下，獲勝的機率是93%(更何況之前的記錄已先掌握一些狀況來判斷了)&nbsp;<br><br>而一般來說，站長希望大家勤作記錄的原因就是和玩紅黑一樣，去判斷最近快要出什麼數字。如果資料完全的話，一般來說，都在5、6次內就會中，再多也不會超過10次。&nbsp;<br><br>普通的話約2小時賺個萬把塊台幣是沒問題的，如果判斷正確的話會更快。&nbsp;<br><br>或是加上紅黑及單雙的押注方式混合運用。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--codes_iframe--><!--/codes_iframe-->			</div>\r\n\r\n						</article>\r\n<article id=\"post-1636\" class=\"post-1636 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail  category-44 single-post-content \">\r\n						<div class=\"post-header post-tp-1-header\">\r\n									<h1 class=\"single-post-title\">\r\n						<span class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">2.輪盤是可以戰勝的</span></h1>\r\n										<div class=\"post-meta-wrap clearfix\">\r\n						<div class=\"term-badges \"><span class=\"term-badge term-44\">輪盤技巧教學</span></div>					</div>\r\n									<div class=\"single-featured\">\r\n									</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n						<div class=\"entry-content clearfix single-post-content\">\r\n				<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_22 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-light-blue\">\r\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\r\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">內容目錄</p>\r\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: inline;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"></i></a></span></div>\r\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"#%E7%99%BE%E5%AE%B6%E6%A8%82%E8%88%87%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4\" title=\"百家樂與輪盤\">百家樂與輪盤</a><ul class=\"ez-toc-list-level-3\"><li class=\"ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"#%E7%BE%8A%E7%BE%A4%E6%95%88%E6%87%89%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%B0%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%97%8E%EF%BC%9F\" title=\"羊群效應就是對的嗎？\">羊群效應就是對的嗎？</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"#%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B8%E4%BA%BA%E7%8E%A9%E7%99%BE%E5%AE%B6%E6%A8%82%E4%BD%A0%E5%B0%B1%E8%A6%81%E8%B7%9F%E8%91%97%E7%8E%A9%E5%97%8E%EF%BC%9F\" title=\"大多數人玩百家樂你就要跟著玩嗎？\">大多數人玩百家樂你就要跟著玩嗎？</a></li></ul></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"#%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%95%E6%B3%A8%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A\" title=\"輪盤的投注機會很多\">輪盤的投注機會很多</a></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-4970 size-large b-loaded\" alt=\"輪盤是可以戰勝的\" width=\"70%\" srcset=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/輪盤是可以戰勝的-1024x680.jpg 1024w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/輪盤是可以戰勝的-300x199.jpg 300w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/輪盤是可以戰勝的-768x510.jpg 768w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/輪盤是可以戰勝的.jpg 1321w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/輪盤是可以戰勝的-1024x680.jpg\">\r\n<figcaption>戰勝賭場輪盤</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-9e3586a4-7b47-41cd-b20d-56ebb83eb5fe\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E7%99%BE%E5%AE%B6%E6%A8%82%E8%88%87%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4\"></span>百家樂與輪盤<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-4de2e954-b700-415a-8575-c05823634dbe\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E7%BE%8A%E7%BE%A4%E6%95%88%E6%87%89%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%B0%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%97%8E%EF%BC%9F\"></span>羊群效應就是對的嗎？<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B8%E4%BA%BA%E7%8E%A9%E7%99%BE%E5%AE%B6%E6%A8%82%E4%BD%A0%E5%B0%B1%E8%A6%81%E8%B7%9F%E8%91%97%E7%8E%A9%E5%97%8E%EF%BC%9F\"></span>大多數人玩百家樂你就要跟著玩嗎？<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>西方人喜歡玩輪盤和撲克，還有角子機，只有在華人世界才會見到以百家樂為主導的賭場。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>我有種感覺，不一定多人玩的就是合理的，或者說就是容易成功的，如果是這樣，更善於計算的西方人會更清楚應該打百家樂，而不是玩輪盤和其他撲克遊戲。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>賭場,百家樂,21點,必勝,賭,賭博雖說百家樂的賭場優勢很小，但它畢竟有8副牌，而且「太公平」了！</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-aa613db4-4c8a-4031-a889-ae11df3968a0\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%95%E6%B3%A8%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A\"></span>輪盤的投注機會很多<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-2c3f9a29-dcb9-4794-88ba-98eff2f43f78\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>輪盤的投注機會很多，更容易找到概率的偏移，而發起攻擊達致贏錢。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>再有，37個號碼，只相當於一副牌，每次都是1/37，百家樂看上去很公平，事實上偏離50/50的時候很多很多，偏向你，你不敢贏，偏離你，你容易輸到足。海百家樂下一局，可以有2億億個組合成為莊/閒，即1/(2億億)，輪盤永遠1/37。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>以前我藐視戴子郎說過百家樂無法破解，也不明白何洛威為什麼不多談百家樂，我現在思想已經有所改觀了，他們可能是對的。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>當然，我也還是認為百家樂也是有機會可以戰勝的，但必須建立在某些苛刻的條件上。其實輪盤和百家樂的賭場優勢差別不大，在澳門你只能打單零輪盤(很好)，無需為雙零擔憂，百家樂有靴之分，其實緊接下一靴還不是隨機的？你也可以按60局輪盤來切割一個賭局段。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>再補充一點，輪盤任何投注區都比百家樂的限紅倍數要低，賭場害怕的正是我們有機會的，這不是很明顯嗎？例如，賭場給你吃給你喝，就是不想你走，害怕你走，而我們偏要懂得走！這就是我們的優勢。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--codes_iframe--><!--/codes_iframe-->			</div>\r\n\r\n						</article>\r\n</div>', '2022-05-27 00:28:45'),
(58, 26, '輪盤技巧教學2', '1.玩輪盤的平均壓注法<br>\r\n2.輪盤壓線打法<br>', NULL, 1, 0, '<div class=\"product\">\r\n<article id=\"post-1634\" class=\"post-1634 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail  category-44 single-post-content \">\r\n						<div class=\"post-header post-tp-1-header\">\r\n									<h1 class=\"single-post-title\">\r\n						<span class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">1.玩輪盤的平均壓注法</span></h1>\r\n										<div class=\"post-meta-wrap clearfix\">\r\n						<div class=\"term-badges \"><span class=\"term-badge term-44\">輪盤技巧教學</span></div>					</div>\r\n									<div class=\"single-featured\">\r\n									</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n						<div class=\"entry-content clearfix single-post-content\">\r\n				<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_22 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-light-blue\">\r\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\r\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">內容目錄</p>\r\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: inline;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"></i></a></span></div>\r\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"#%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E8%BC%83%E5%B0%8F%E7%9A%84%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E4%B8%8B%E6%B3%A8%E6%B3%95\" title=\"風險較小的輪盤下注法\">風險較小的輪盤下注法</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"#%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E4%B8%8B%E6%B3%A8%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5\" title=\"輪盤下注策略\">輪盤下注策略</a></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img width=\"70%\" class=\"wp-image-1628 b-loaded\" alt=\"輪盤技巧＿平均壓注法 \" srcset=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/gambling-2001032_1920-1-1024x539.jpg 1024w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/gambling-2001032_1920-1-300x158.jpg 300w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/gambling-2001032_1920-1-768x404.jpg 768w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/gambling-2001032_1920-1-720x380.jpg 720w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/gambling-2001032_1920-1.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/gambling-2001032_1920-1-1024x539.jpg\">\r\n<figcaption>平均壓注法</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-f9f3d141-0d0d-4f1b-9bd4-d91aedc41cc8\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E8%BC%83%E5%B0%8F%E7%9A%84%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E4%B8%8B%E6%B3%A8%E6%B3%95\"></span>風險較小的輪盤下注法<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-4afb1aef-19d9-4202-8196-ca1e97000ce7\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>平注法相對來說風險比較小，因為每把的下注額固定，回報也固定。賭的是每把壓注你的命中概率為2/3，也就是在36個數字中壓24個數字左右。而24個數字的選取則根據當前輪盤的歷史數據，選擇出現概率最大的24個數字或者數字所在的區間。這裡的第一和第二中方式都是平注法，以希望在多次的壓注過程中對莊家取得領先。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>事實上，根據數學家的計算,單零的輪盤賭場優勢是百分之二點七，即是每玩一百元，你大概會輸去二點七元，轉去雙零輪盤。賭場優勢更會激增近一倍至百分之五點二。所以有可能情況下必須玩單零的賭局。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>觀察輪盤出現的前36次結果，看1~12，13~24，25~36出現的次數比較結果。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>切記切記，如果0和00出現次數累計超過一次的話，轉台。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>如果某兩個區間出現次數明顯多過另一個區間的話（如1~12出20次，13~24出18次，25~36出8次）</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-6d6cffcd-a66d-41a7-9446-d555f79188f6\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E4%B8%8B%E6%B3%A8%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5\"></span>輪盤下注策略<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-c8124e40-77cc-4c1a-9fee-e68fae9d71c8\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>準備200元作為本金，1~12 壓注 40元，13~24壓注40元，觀察最近出的紅黑走向，判別為紅壓5元在9、12的split，否則壓8、11的split，然後壓5元在2、3、5、6的對角線（基於前面出現數字中沒有1、4出現過，但有3、6出現）。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>始終保持outside和inside對比40/5＝8的倍數，因為有超過2/3的贏錢概率，所以非常容易贏錢。準備200元可以保持兩次不超過4/38的連續輸錢概率。壓注總額90元，每次贏30元，回報率非常可觀，每次inside的split的壓注要考慮紅黑走向，然後以36次壓注為一個基本壓注週期，任何一個週期沒有贏利則退出，0出現兩次以上也退出。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--codes_iframe--><!--/codes_iframe-->			</div>\r\n\r\n						</article><article id=\"post-1625\" class=\"post-1625 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail  category-44 single-post-content \">\r\n						<div class=\"post-header post-tp-1-header\">\r\n									<h1 class=\"single-post-title\">\r\n						<span class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">2.輪盤壓線打法</span></h1>\r\n										<div class=\"post-meta-wrap clearfix\">\r\n						<div class=\"term-badges \"><span class=\"term-badge term-44\"></span></div>					</div>\r\n									<div class=\"single-featured\">\r\n									</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n						<div class=\"entry-content clearfix single-post-content\">\r\n				<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_22 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-light-blue\">\r\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\r\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">內容目錄</p>\r\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: inline;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"></i></a></span></div>\r\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"#%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E5%A3%93%E7%B7%9A%E6%89%93%E6%B3%95%E8%AB%96%E9%BB%9E1\" title=\"輪盤壓線打法論點1\">輪盤壓線打法論點1</a><ul class=\"ez-toc-list-level-3\"><li class=\"ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"#%E3%80%8C%E9%9B%B6%E3%80%8D%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E5%A7%8B%E7%B5%82%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%A0%E7%9F%A5%E6%88%91%E7%9F%A5%E8%B3%AD%E5%A0%B4%E9%83%BD%E7%9F%A5%E3%80%82\" title=\"「零」風險始終存在，你知我知賭場都知。\">「零」風險始終存在，你知我知賭場都知。</a></li></ul></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"#%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E5%A3%93%E7%B7%9A%E6%89%93%E6%B3%95%E8%AB%96%E9%BB%9E2\" title=\"輪盤壓線打法論點2\">輪盤壓線打法論點2</a></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-4970 size-large b-loaded\" alt=\"輪盤是可以戰勝的\" width=\"70%\" srcset=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/輪盤是可以戰勝的-1024x680.jpg 1024w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/輪盤是可以戰勝的-300x199.jpg 300w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/輪盤是可以戰勝的-768x510.jpg 768w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/輪盤是可以戰勝的.jpg 1321w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/輪盤是可以戰勝的-1024x680.jpg\"><br>\r\n<figcaption>輪盤技巧：壓線打法</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-d73c5509-8430-4829-befe-26efa8b4b070\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>不是一種必勝打法，也不是我發明的打法，只是對此法有些觀點想和各位討論一下。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>顧名思義壓線就是，把籌碼壓在邊線上，只要和邊線相關的號碼中，則有收穫。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-b04509fb-2e6b-4f86-a45c-d282d4d20e38\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E5%A3%93%E7%B7%9A%E6%89%93%E6%B3%95%E8%AB%96%E9%BB%9E1\"></span>輪盤壓線打法論點1<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-89000bf5-d171-4151-baa3-1cad78afc62d\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>如果你使用6個碼，分別壓在不相干的6條線上，（1，4）（7，10）（13，16）（19，22）（25，28）（31，34），那麼只要不開零，收穫也是零，賺個玩。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>論點1表面上看沒有什麼好處，其實可以用來打分，好多時候，未見到零，已經打夠積分了。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E3%80%8C%E9%9B%B6%E3%80%8D%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E5%A7%8B%E7%B5%82%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%A0%E7%9F%A5%E6%88%91%E7%9F%A5%E8%B3%AD%E5%A0%B4%E9%83%BD%E7%9F%A5%E3%80%82\"></span>「零」風險始終存在，你知我知賭場都知。<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>同樣的打分方法還可以這樣，紅黑各買300，零買20，開零賺100，開紅黑輸20，可以看好紅黑的稍買大少許。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>打分有什麼用？有些賭場每天都有抽獎或現金回贈，有人就是衝著這個來的，不說抽獎，每天打分拿現金回贈100多元不是問題，如果說到抽獎，中個幾千元的手機或幾十萬的小轎車都不是假的.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>金沙最近每天都搞滾動百萬抽獎就是要憑積分拿抽獎券，最低獎是1萬元.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>有次我在星際，有個肥鬼佬3個小時就中了3次獎，約3萬元。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>輪盤是某些老鼠的打分工具。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-462f3d60-f83b-4d90-8306-78e75642589a\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E5%A3%93%E7%B7%9A%E6%89%93%E6%B3%95%E8%AB%96%E9%BB%9E2\"></span>輪盤壓線打法論點2<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-699d0931-329c-491b-a688-bd0b5e9c37c7\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>如果你使用4個碼，分別壓在不相干的4條線上，結果是2賠1，就是中了賠一半，相當於玩3區買2區。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>論壇上的各種3區買2區打法和論點2是殊途同歸，只不過論點2就可以靈活些，將12個號的大區變成6個號的小區，可以去追旺號。如果把握得好，小賺些錢還是不錯的。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>有些人玩壓線是亂壓一通，輸贏都不甚了了，等同自殺。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--codes_iframe--><!--/codes_iframe-->			</div>\r\n\r\n						</article></div>', '2022-05-27 00:28:45'),
(59, 26, '輪盤技巧教學3', '1.輪盤賭博線上賭場的投注法則<br>\r\n2.一位職業賭徒的輪盤小技巧', NULL, 1, 0, '<div class=\"product\">\r\n<article id=\"post-1631\" class=\"post-1631 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail  category-44 single-post-content \">\r\n						<div class=\"post-header post-tp-1-header\">\r\n									<h1 class=\"single-post-title\">\r\n						<span class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">1.輪盤賭博線上賭場的投注法則</span></h1>\r\n										<div class=\"post-meta-wrap clearfix\">\r\n						<div class=\"term-badges \"><span class=\"term-badge term-44\">輪盤技巧教學</span></div>					</div>\r\n									<div class=\"single-featured\">\r\n									</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n						<div class=\"entry-content clearfix single-post-content\">\r\n				<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_22 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-light-blue\">\r\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\r\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">內容目錄</p>\r\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: inline;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"></i></a></span></div>\r\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><ul class=\"ez-toc-list-level-3\"><li class=\"ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"#%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E8%B3%AD%E5%8D%9A%E6%88%90%E5%B0%B1%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%8D%9A%E5%BD%A9%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%80%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%81%E4%BD%86%E6%94%B6%E7%9B%8A%E6%9C%80%E5%B7%AE%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E8%AB%96%EF%BC%8D%E9%A6%AC%E4%B8%81%E6%A0%BC%E7%88%BE%E6%B3%95%E5%89%87%E3%80%82\" title=\"輪盤賭博成就了世界博彩業中最流行、但收益最差的理論－馬丁格爾法則。\">輪盤賭博成就了世界博彩業中最流行、但收益最差的理論－馬丁格爾法則。</a></li></ul><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"#%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E9%A6%AC%E4%B8%81%E6%A0%BC%E7%88%BE%E6%B3%95%E5%89%87%E6%8A%95%E6%B3%A8%E6%B3%95\" title=\"輪盤馬丁格爾法則投注法\">輪盤馬丁格爾法則投注法</a><ul class=\"ez-toc-list-level-3\"><li class=\"ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"#%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E9%A6%AC%E4%B8%81%E6%A0%BC%E7%88%BE%E6%B3%95%E5%89%87\" title=\"輪盤馬丁格爾法則\">輪盤馬丁格爾法則</a></li></ul></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"#%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E7%A9%8D%E6%A5%B5%E6%8A%95%E6%B3%A8%E6%B3%95%E5%AF%A6%E4%BE%8B\" title=\"輪盤積極投注法實例\">輪盤積極投注法實例</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"#%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8B%E6%B3%A8%E6%B3%95%E5%89%87\" title=\"輪盤成功的下注法則\">輪盤成功的下注法則</a></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-4974 size-large b-loaded\" alt=\"輪盤是可以戰勝的\" width=\"70%\" srcset=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/輪盤是可以戰勝的-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/輪盤是可以戰勝的-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/輪盤是可以戰勝的-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/輪盤是可以戰勝的-1.jpg 1328w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/輪盤是可以戰勝的-1-1024x683.jpg\">\r\n<figcaption>賭網上輪盤賭的投注法則</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-20fd9ea5-c402-43e2-b4aa-c53a918b9120\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E8%B3%AD%E5%8D%9A%E6%88%90%E5%B0%B1%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%8D%9A%E5%BD%A9%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%80%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%81%E4%BD%86%E6%94%B6%E7%9B%8A%E6%9C%80%E5%B7%AE%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E8%AB%96%EF%BC%8D%E9%A6%AC%E4%B8%81%E6%A0%BC%E7%88%BE%E6%B3%95%E5%89%87%E3%80%82\"></span>輪盤賭博成就了世界博彩業中最流行、但收益最差的理論－馬丁格爾法則。<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>儘管不推薦馬丁格爾法則，其他的一些有益方法還是值得嘗試。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-84237240-8d57-4047-b2f2-9a3dea387aff\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E9%A6%AC%E4%B8%81%E6%A0%BC%E7%88%BE%E6%B3%95%E5%89%87%E6%8A%95%E6%B3%A8%E6%B3%95\"></span>輪盤馬丁格爾法則投注法<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-6602914e-f199-4a15-9634-3e812737a699\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E9%A6%AC%E4%B8%81%E6%A0%BC%E7%88%BE%E6%B3%95%E5%89%87\"></span>輪盤馬丁格爾法則<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>建議您輸後加倍，但是積極投注法卻正好相反，贏後加倍，後者的積極性不言而喻，因為您可以在鴻運當頭時乘勝追擊，即使手氣轉霉，也不過把贏來的錢輸掉而已。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>其實也就是拿您賺來的錢碰運氣。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>然而馬丁格爾法則中，您是拿自己的錢去賭風險，很容易就打了水漂。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-25139fdd-8ccd-48ca-a0ce-2899264765d0\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E7%A9%8D%E6%A5%B5%E6%8A%95%E6%B3%A8%E6%B3%95%E5%AF%A6%E4%BE%8B\"></span>輪盤積極投注法實例<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-46f84597-c703-4948-ac05-7f8d7c35f52d\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>如果您想試試積極投注法，可以參考下面的投注戰術。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>對5個不同的號碼各投一個籌碼，如果一個都沒中，如此重復投注直到押中一個為止。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>一旦押中一個數字，您就能贏回30個籌碼。接下來每個號碼再增加一個籌碼，如果命中，您就收穫60個籌碼，加上先前的30個，您就贏了90個。如果沒有命中，您還剩20個籌碼。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>繼續如此投注，直到20個籌碼也都輸光，然後重新開始每號一個籌碼。這樣的積極投注法可以讓您迅速積累更多的籌碼，同時所冒的風險也是在您的承受範圍之內。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-a27e7b24-c910-4e07-a330-e693032187bb\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8B%E6%B3%A8%E6%B3%95%E5%89%87\"></span>輪盤成功的下注法則<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-8d14dcc4-092c-499e-bd66-380a34428bbf\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>記住，賭場不會做虧本買賣，即使輪盤賭他們也會有一定的收益率，因此運氣還是相當重要。如果您運氣不錯，採用積極投注法能夠讓您的好運變成實實在在的金錢。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--codes_iframe--><!--/codes_iframe-->			</div>\r\n\r\n						</article>\r\n<article id=\"post-2248\" class=\"post-2248 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail  category-44 single-post-content \">\r\n						<div class=\"post-header post-tp-1-header\">\r\n									<h1 class=\"single-post-title\">\r\n						<span class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">一位職業賭徒的輪盤小技巧</span></h1>\r\n										<div class=\"post-meta-wrap clearfix\">\r\n						<div class=\"term-badges \"><span class=\"term-badge term-44\">輪盤技巧教學</span></div>					</div>\r\n									<div class=\"single-featured\">\r\n									</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n						<div class=\"entry-content clearfix single-post-content\">\r\n				<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_22 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-light-blue\">\r\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\r\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">內容目錄</p>\r\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: inline;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"></i></a></span></div>\r\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"#%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E4%B8%8B%E6%B3%A8%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7\" title=\"輪盤下注技巧\">輪盤下注技巧</a><ul class=\"ez-toc-list-level-3\"><li class=\"ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"#%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5\" title=\"輪盤攻略\">輪盤攻略</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"#%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87\" title=\"輪盤投資\">輪盤投資</a></li></ul></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-4867 size-full b-loaded\" alt=\"輪盤下注技巧\" width=\"70%\" srcset=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/輪盤下注技巧.jpg 1334w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/輪盤下注技巧-300x199.jpg 300w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/輪盤下注技巧-1024x681.jpg 1024w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/輪盤下注技巧-768x511.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1334px) 100vw, 1334px\" src=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/輪盤下注技巧.jpg\">\r\n<figcaption>一位職業賭徒的輪盤小技巧</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-3e4eca7c-496a-439c-8d51-5dd54ffae027\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E4%B8%8B%E6%B3%A8%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7\"></span>輪盤下注技巧<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-893164cd-e99e-4d28-9df0-1651bb588d55\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5\"></span>輪盤攻略<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>對於輪盤這個遊戲大家一直堅信它是靠運氣的取勝的遊戲，因為我們經常很難猜測小球在哪裡停住，總是會在心裡默念願上帝保佑我吧。其實輪盤也並不是全靠技巧的，我們可以在遊戲中仔細觀察出一些小的技巧來，曾經聽一位前輩說過他的經驗，就是研究莊家。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87\"></span>輪盤投資<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>他幾乎天天都到賭場，對一些老莊家的偏好已經熟悉了。每次他到賭場不是馬上就賭，一般先對莊家的投球方式以及輪盤轉速等觀察一陣，大概就能熟悉莊家的特點了。在莊家發球的一瞬間，他在心裡默默對球的落點快速預測，如果連續幾次均猜得比較准，就要一決勝負了。他每天帶一百元到賭場，先買二十個一元的籌碼，如果他認為球可能落在8，就會在8及8左右的號碼上投注，即他會在6,18,31,19，8，12，29，25，10，27這十個號碼各投兩個一元籌碼，總共二十元，這樣又大大提供了命中率。只要中了一個號碼，他就可以得到2元X 35＝70元。他帶來的錢放在左口袋，贏了的錢就放進右口袋。真人娛樂場他如果贏了七十元，就把五十元放進右口袋，剩下的二十元繼續以這種方式賭。如果沒贏，他就再從左口袋再掏出二十元，如果帶來的一百元用完了，他就打道回府了，決不用掏右口袋的錢來賭，這樣他平均每天能賺一百多加幣，就象打一份工一樣，屢試不爽。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>不知道這個研究你感覺怎樣？趕緊去試一下把！</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--codes_iframe--><!--/codes_iframe-->			</div>\r\n\r\n						</article></div>', '2022-05-27 00:28:45');
INSERT INTO `product` (`p_id`, `classid`, `p_name`, `p_intro`, `p_price`, `p_open`, `p_cart`, `p_content`, `p_date`) VALUES
(60, 26, '線上輪盤遊戲玩家玩法分享', '1.線上輪盤遊戲玩家玩法分享<br>\r\n2.玩家分享1輪盤遊戲必勝玩法', NULL, 1, 0, '<div class=\"product\">\r\n<article id=\"post-2614\" class=\"post-2614 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail  category-44 single-post-content \">\r\n						<div class=\"post-header post-tp-1-header\">\r\n									<h1 class=\"single-post-title\">\r\n						<span class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">1.線上輪盤遊戲玩家玩法分享</span></h1>\r\n										<div class=\"post-meta-wrap clearfix\">\r\n						<div class=\"term-badges \"><span class=\"term-badge term-44\">輪盤技巧教學</a></span></div>					</div>\r\n									<div class=\"single-featured\">\r\n									</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n						<div class=\"entry-content clearfix single-post-content\">\r\n				<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_22 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-light-blue\">\r\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\r\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">內容目錄</p>\r\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: inline;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"></i></a></span></div>\r\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"#%E7%B7%9A%E4%B8%8A%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\" title=\"線上輪盤遊戲分享前言\">線上輪盤遊戲分享前言</a><ul class=\"ez-toc-list-level-3\"><li class=\"ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"#%E6%89%93%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%8A%E6%98%AF%E6%8A%93%E5%AD%A4%E4%B8%81%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%93%E7%86%B1%E5%8D%80\" title=\"打的方法基本上是抓孤丁，打熱區\">打的方法基本上是抓孤丁，打熱區</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"#%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E5%96%9C%E6%AD%A1%E6%89%930%E5%8D%80%EF%BC%8C%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%A4%E5%96%9C%E6%AD%A1%E6%89%93%E5%8D%8A%E5%8D%80%E7%B4%85%E9%BB%91\" title=\"亞洲輪盤喜歡打0區，歐盤喜歡打半區紅黑\">亞洲輪盤喜歡打0區，歐盤喜歡打半區紅黑</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"#%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E8%B3%A0%E7%8E%87%E7%8E%A9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%9A\" title=\"保持賠率玩法：\">保持賠率玩法：</a></li></ul></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"#%E7%B7%9A%E4%B8%8A%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%B6%E7%B6%93%E9%A9%97%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB\" title=\"線上輪盤遊戲玩家經驗分享\">線上輪盤遊戲玩家經驗分享</a></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-4804 size-full b-loaded\" alt=\"線上輪盤遊戲之玩家玩法分享\" width=\"70%\" srcset=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/超級盃輪盤大賽.jpg 1177w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/超級盃輪盤大賽-300x223.jpg 300w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/超級盃輪盤大賽-1024x761.jpg 1024w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/超級盃輪盤大賽-768x571.jpg 768w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/超級盃輪盤大賽-86x64.jpg 86w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1177px) 100vw, 1177px\" src=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/超級盃輪盤大賽.jpg\">\r\n<figcaption>線上輪盤玩家玩法分享</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-04653ae0-3ad5-4843-bd3d-3cc6f557b688\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E7%B7%9A%E4%B8%8A%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\"></span>線上輪盤遊戲分享前言<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-591cb6cc-bdc1-47b3-9fc4-037ec8059c09\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>打網上輪盤六七年了，比百家樂歷史還長，有過幾次經典戰役，不過最終都是體無完膚，各位不要見笑，</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>有過30塊錢打到1萬，150塊錢打到1萬，500塊錢打到6萬，2000塊錢打到4萬發生過很多次，1萬塊錢打到10幾萬也時不時來一次，在澳門用過3千5人民幣打到17萬港幣，最終都是輸，止不住贏，錢只是個數字！</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E6%89%93%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%8A%E6%98%AF%E6%8A%93%E5%AD%A4%E4%B8%81%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%93%E7%86%B1%E5%8D%80\"></span>打的方法基本上是抓孤丁，打熱區<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E5%96%9C%E6%AD%A1%E6%89%930%E5%8D%80%EF%BC%8C%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%A4%E5%96%9C%E6%AD%A1%E6%89%93%E5%8D%8A%E5%8D%80%E7%B4%85%E9%BB%91\"></span>亞洲輪盤喜歡打0區，歐盤喜歡打半區紅黑<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E8%B3%A0%E7%8E%87%E7%8E%A9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%9A\"></span>保持賠率玩法：<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>（例如一邊打25，34，27，30，23，另一邊打28，29，22，20，24），一般不會打超過9個以上的孤丁，保持賠率在1：4或以上，低於這個賠率就不如去打百家樂了，對否？</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>處女帖，與各位大仙交流！</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-30f37a47-e3a4-40ee-99f7-0f47064204d1\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E7%B7%9A%E4%B8%8A%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%B6%E7%B6%93%E9%A9%97%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB\"></span>線上輪盤遊戲玩家經驗分享<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-e7fe8e97-cad7-4466-ad2d-7f168e4d182b\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>玩家A：波音基本上沒打過，以前在上面玩過百家樂，不太信得過波音。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>玩家B：其實我還是喜歡EA的平台的，有亞洲盤和歐洲盤兩種可以先擇，HG統一都是歐洲盤，有時候下風時，換一個盤來打也能抵抗一下下風。早期的EA孤丁是不限注的，我記得幾年前有一局我投注不超過4000，但派彩派了近7萬。後來才有孤丁單獨限注。HG有一點好處是對冷熱號有提示，不像EA，一次只能顯示50局，要想看冷熱號，要一個個去比對，累的要死，自己又不會寫軟件，只能拿筆記，在澳門，有一個晚上，記了大概400多局，找冷熱號，頭都看暈了。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>玩家C：那個帖子主要目的是洩一口氣，前面存了2500去大東方，媽的，孤丁最高25，想提款，要打流水，去百家樂，黑光光。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>玩家D：我又比較強牛，在百家樂上輸掉2500，就想在百家樂上打回來，又存了2500到鴻運去打百家樂，又黑光光。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>後來一想，這不是錯上加錯嘛，本來就是準備打輪盤的，被場子這麼一搞，去掉了5000在百家樂身上。還是專心打輪盤吧，存了5000專打輪盤才慢慢打上去。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--codes_iframe--><!--/codes_iframe-->			</div>\r\n<article id=\"post-2611\" class=\"post-2611 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail  category-44 single-post-content \">\r\n						<div class=\"post-header post-tp-1-header\">\r\n									<h1 class=\"single-post-title\">\r\n						<span class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">2.玩家分享1輪盤遊戲必勝玩法</span></h1>\r\n										<div class=\"post-meta-wrap clearfix\">\r\n						<div class=\"term-badges \"><span class=\"term-badge term-44\">輪盤技巧教學</a></span></div>					</div>\r\n									<div class=\"single-featured\">\r\n									</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n						<div class=\"entry-content clearfix single-post-content\">\r\n				<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_22 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-light-blue\">\r\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\r\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">內容目錄</p>\r\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: inline;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"></i></a></span></div>\r\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"#%E6%88%91%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E8%B4%8F%E9%8C%A2%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8B%E6%B3%A8%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%9A%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E9%A0%90%E6%B8%AC\" title=\"我一個輪盤贏錢的下注方法：輪盤分析預測\">我一個輪盤贏錢的下注方法：輪盤分析預測</a></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4807 size-large b-loaded\" alt=\"分享1個輪盤遊戲必勝玩法\" width=\"70%\" srcset=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/分享1個輪盤遊戲必勝玩法-1024x662.jpg 1024w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/分享1個輪盤遊戲必勝玩法-300x194.jpg 300w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/分享1個輪盤遊戲必勝玩法-768x496.jpg 768w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/分享1個輪盤遊戲必勝玩法-210x136.jpg 210w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/分享1個輪盤遊戲必勝玩法.jpg 1342w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/分享1個輪盤遊戲必勝玩法-1024x662.jpg\">\r\n<figcaption>玩家分享輪盤遊戲必勝法</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-989b79ae-4634-426e-b598-28921f598e4a\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E6%88%91%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E8%B4%8F%E9%8C%A2%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8B%E6%B3%A8%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%9A%E8%BC%AA%E7%9B%A4%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E9%A0%90%E6%B8%AC\"></span>我一個輪盤贏錢的下注方法：輪盤分析預測<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-3cac812f-f392-470a-84fc-e52b5a48a25d\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>是3把內贏1把靠譜還是30把內贏10把靠譜？</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>假定30把內必贏10把，或假定30把內必開10把閒。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>第一把下10，輸，&nbsp; 把輸的10分攤到剩餘預計10把要贏的注碼中，第二把下&nbsp;&nbsp; 10+10/10=11，暫計劃剩餘29把每把下11。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>第二把下11，輸，把輸的11分攤到剩餘預計10把要贏的注碼中，剩餘28把計劃下11+11/10=12.1,於是第三把下12.1</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>第三把下12.1，贏，第四把繼續下12.1</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>第四把下12.1，輸，下把下12.1+12.1/9(贏過1把，還剩9把可以贏）</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>依此類推，30把內有贏2個碼左右就馬上割禾</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--codes_iframe--><!--/codes_iframe-->			</div>\r\n\r\n						</article>\r\n\r\n						</article>\r\n</div>', '2022-05-27 00:28:45'),
(61, 27, '骰寶技巧教學1', '骰子擲好運 Chuck-A-Luck 遊戲規則', NULL, 1, 0, '<div class=\"product\"><article id=\"post-1512\" class=\"post-1512 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail  category-48 single-post-content \">\r\n						<div class=\"post-header post-tp-1-header\">\r\n									<h1 class=\"single-post-title\">\r\n						<span class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">骰子擲好運 Chuck-A-Luck 遊戲規則</span></h1>\r\n										<div class=\"post-meta-wrap clearfix\">\r\n						<div class=\"term-badges \"><span class=\"term-badge term-48\">骰寶技巧教學</span></div>					</div>\r\n									<div class=\"single-featured\">\r\n									</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n						<div class=\"entry-content clearfix single-post-content\">\r\n				<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_22 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-light-blue\">\r\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\r\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">內容目錄</p>\r\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: inline;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"></i></a></span></div>\r\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"#%E9%AA%B0%E5%AD%90%E6%93%B2%E5%A5%BD%E9%81%8B%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87Chuck-A-Luck_%E8%B3%AD%E6%A1%8C%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2\" title=\"骰子擲好運規則(Chuck-A-Luck) ( 賭桌遊戲 )\">骰子擲好運規則(Chuck-A-Luck) ( 賭桌遊戲 )</a><ul class=\"ez-toc-list-level-3\"><li class=\"ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"#%E6%93%B2%E5%A5%BD%E9%81%8B%E9%AA%B0%E5%AD%90%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E4%BB%8B%E7%B4%B9\" title=\"擲好運骰子遊戲介紹\">擲好運骰子遊戲介紹</a></li></ul></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"#%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B%E7%8E%A9%E9%AA%B0%E5%AD%90%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2\" title=\" 開始玩骰子遊戲\"> 開始玩骰子遊戲</a><ul class=\"ez-toc-list-level-3\"><li class=\"ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"#%E6%93%B2%E5%A5%BD%E9%81%8B%E9%AA%B0%E5%AD%90%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87\" title=\"擲好運骰子基本規則\">擲好運骰子基本規則</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"#%E9%AA%B0%E5%AD%90%E6%93%B2%E5%A5%BD%E9%81%8B%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B6%E7%A8%AE%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8B%E6%B3%A8%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E8%88%87%E8%B3%A0%E7%8E%87\" title=\" 骰子擲好運遊戲提供6種不同的下注方法與賠率: \"> 骰子擲好運遊戲提供6種不同的下注方法與賠率: </a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"#%E8%B3%AD%E8%99%9F%E7%A2%BC\" title=\"賭號碼\">賭號碼</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"#%E8%B3%AD%E7%B8%BD%E9%BB%9E\" title=\"賭總點\">賭總點</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"#%E8%B3%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%A7%E6%96%BC10\" title=\"賭大(大於10)\">賭大(大於10)</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"#%E8%B3%AD%E5%B0%8F%E5%B0%8F%E6%96%BC11\" title=\"賭小(小於11)\">賭小(小於11)</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"#%E8%B3%AD%E5%96%AE\" title=\"賭單\">賭單</a></li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"#%E8%B3%AD%E9%9B%99\" title=\"賭雙\">賭雙</a></li></ul></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-4988 size-large b-loaded\" alt=\"二骰賭博（craps）規則\" width=\"70%\" srcset=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/二骰賭博（craps）規則-1024x673.jpg 1024w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/二骰賭博（craps）規則-300x197.jpg 300w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/二骰賭博（craps）規則-768x504.jpg 768w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/二骰賭博（craps）規則.jpg 1311w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/二骰賭博（craps）規則-1024x673.jpg\">\r\n<figcaption>二骰賭博（craps）</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-c339a566-97af-43a1-a80f-9051283376e1\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E9%AA%B0%E5%AD%90%E6%93%B2%E5%A5%BD%E9%81%8B%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87Chuck-A-Luck_%E8%B3%AD%E6%A1%8C%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2\"></span>骰子擲好運規則(Chuck-A-Luck) ( 賭桌遊戲 )<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-48186ac1-50be-42a3-abe8-78423514a3f1\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E6%93%B2%E5%A5%BD%E9%81%8B%E9%AA%B0%E5%AD%90%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E4%BB%8B%E7%B4%B9\"></span>擲好運骰子遊戲介紹<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>骰子擲好運是一種非常有趣的骰子遊戲，玩法是晃動骰盒，使三個骰子在盒中翻滾，然後看賭骰盒停下後骰子如何落定。此遊戲可能是在多年前源於英國,開始時並沒有骰盒.賭徒用金屬制的或皮制的角形賭具在賭桌上擲三個骰子,骰子如何落定決定了他們的輸贏.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>一個有趣的說明就是金屬賭具比皮制賭具流行–而錫又比黃銅便宜–而經常設賭的人錢又不多,這也就是為什麼當時的金屬賭具又稱”錫角賭棍”.&nbsp;<br>時至今日,在狂歡節,一些籌資活動和許多一流賭博娛樂場中,擲骰子遊戲非常受歡迎.對新手而言, 擲骰子遊戲非常簡單易學.而對老手來說,此遊戲富有刺激而且贏率高.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-5f6e9d51-e5db-4ea0-a28f-a16897b3e36c\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B%E7%8E%A9%E9%AA%B0%E5%AD%90%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2\"></span><strong> 開始玩骰子遊戲</strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-c770054b-153c-4e1c-81e6-9d30a5139d8e\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E6%93%B2%E5%A5%BD%E9%81%8B%E9%AA%B0%E5%AD%90%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87\"></span>擲好運骰子基本規則<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>骰子是標準的六面立方體，各面數位分別為 1 至 6(一面有多少個點就代表多少數字)。骰盒裡共有三個骰子,骰盒繞水準軸轉動,骰子在盒內晃動.玩家把籌碼放到賭桌上各區域進行投注.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>在至少有一注下注後,骰盒才可以轉動.玩家下注完畢後，可按一下”旋轉”按鈕開始遊戲.這時所有下注必須暫停.幾秒鐘後骰盒停止轉動,三個骰子停在骰盒底部.每個骰子頂麵點數之和就是賭局的結果.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E9%AA%B0%E5%AD%90%E6%93%B2%E5%A5%BD%E9%81%8B%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B6%E7%A8%AE%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8B%E6%B3%A8%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E8%88%87%E8%B3%A0%E7%8E%87\"></span><strong> 骰子擲好運遊戲提供6種不同的下注方法與賠率: </strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>賭號碼&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>賭總點&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>賭大(大於10)&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>賭小(小於11)&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;賭單&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>賭雙</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E8%B3%AD%E8%99%9F%E7%A2%BC\"></span><strong><span class=\"tadv-color\" style=\"color: #cf2e2e;\">賭號碼</span></strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>“賭號碼”共有6個號碼下注區(1, 2, 3, 4, 5 和 6).根據多少個骰子出現您賭的號碼決定您能贏多少.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>中號骰子&nbsp;賠率<br>1 (一中)&nbsp;1:1<br>2 (雙中)&nbsp;2:1<br>3 (三中)&nbsp;10:1</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>若所有三個骰子開出的數字是4，賭號碼4的下注賠率為：1 賠 10。您可以同時賭多個號碼。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>其餘的5種下注方法都是基於三個骰子開出的點數之和.例如,三個骰子開出的結果分別為 5點, 2點,4點; 總點數為11. 總點數在 3(三個1點) 和18(三個6點)之間.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E8%B3%AD%E7%B8%BD%E9%BB%9E\"></span><strong><span class=\"tadv-color\" style=\"color: #cf2e2e;\">賭總點</span></strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>如果您在“總和下注”區中下注，則是賭所有三個骰子的總點數是否是“總和下注”區中的某個數字。無論您將賭注放在“總和下注”區中的哪個位置，只要骰子的總點數是“總和下注”區內的任何一個數字，您就會獲賠 1 倍的賭金。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E8%B3%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%A7%E6%96%BC10\"></span><span class=\"tadv-color\" style=\"color: #cf2e2e;\"><strong>賭大(大於10)</strong></span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>如您”賭大”,您就是賭三個骰子總點數大於10.賠率是1:1 ; 但出現大”三同號”時(12, 15 或 18),”賭大”輸錢. 三個骰子總點數大於10有 108種可能組合,而出現大”三同號”只有3種組合.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E8%B3%AD%E5%B0%8F%E5%B0%8F%E6%96%BC11\"></span><span class=\"tadv-color\" style=\"color: #cf2e2e;\"><strong>賭小(小於11)</strong></span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>如您”賭小”,您就是賭三個骰子總點數小於11.賠率是1:1 ; 但出現小”三同號”時(3, 6 或 9),”賭小”輸錢. 三個骰子總點數小於11有 108種可能組合,而出現小”三同號”只有3種組合.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E8%B3%AD%E5%96%AE\"></span><span class=\"tadv-color\" style=\"color: #cf2e2e;\"><strong>賭單</strong></span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>如您”賭單”,您就是賭三個骰子總點數為奇數.賠率是1:1 ;但出現奇數”三同號”時(3, 9 或 15),”賭單”輸錢. 三個骰子總點數為奇數有108種可能組合,而出現奇數”三同號”只有3種組合.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E8%B3%AD%E9%9B%99\"></span><strong><span class=\"tadv-color\" style=\"color: #cf2e2e;\">賭雙</span></strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>如您”賭雙”,您就是賭三個骰子總點數為偶數.賠率是1:1 ;但出現偶數”三同號”時(6, 12 或 18),”賭雙”輸錢. 三個骰子總點數為偶數有108種可能組合,而出現偶數”三同號”只有3種組合.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!--codes_iframe--><!--/codes_iframe-->			</div>\r\n\r\n						</article>\r\n</div>', '2022-06-07 00:55:42'),
(62, 27, '骰寶技巧教學2', '三軍10式直纜心法', NULL, 1, 0, '<div class=\"product\"><article id=\"post-2705\" class=\"post-2705 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail  category-48 single-post-content \">\r\n						<div class=\"post-header post-tp-1-header\">\r\n									<h1 class=\"single-post-title\">\r\n						<span class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">骰寶技巧：三軍10式直纜心法</span></h1>\r\n										<div class=\"post-meta-wrap clearfix\">\r\n						<div class=\"term-badges \"><span class=\"term-badge term-48\">骰寶技巧教學</span></div>					</div>\r\n									<div class=\"single-featured\">\r\n									</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n						<div class=\"entry-content clearfix single-post-content\">\r\n				<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_22 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-light-blue\">\r\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\r\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">內容目錄</p>\r\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: inline;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"></i></a></span></div>\r\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"#%E9%AA%B0%E5%AF%B6%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7%EF%BC%9A_%E4%B8%89%E8%BB%8D10%E5%BC%8F%E7%9B%B4%E7%BA%9C%E5%BF%83%E6%B3%95%E6%8A%95%E6%B3%A8%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F\" title=\"骰寶技巧： 三軍10式直纜心法投注方式\">骰寶技巧： 三軍10式直纜心法投注方式</a><ul class=\"ez-toc-list-level-3\"><li class=\"ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"#%E6%8A%95%E6%B3%A8%E5%BF%83%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%9A\" title=\"投注心法：\">投注心法：</a></li></ul></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-608c9bf6-89c0-4599-baa1-1e240c29c52b\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E9%AA%B0%E5%AF%B6%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7%EF%BC%9A_%E4%B8%89%E8%BB%8D10%E5%BC%8F%E7%9B%B4%E7%BA%9C%E5%BF%83%E6%B3%95%E6%8A%95%E6%B3%A8%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F\"></span><strong>骰寶技巧：</strong> <strong>三軍10式直纜心法</strong>投注方式<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-d3f26795-f0e8-4cba-aa7c-269dff8f3c8d\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p><strong>期數&nbsp; 本期投注&nbsp; 若不中累計盈亐&nbsp; 若中累計盈虧</strong></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;1&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 100&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 100&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 100<br>&nbsp;2&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 150&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 250&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 50<br>&nbsp;3&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 300&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 550&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 50<br>&nbsp;4&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 600&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1150&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 50<br>&nbsp;5&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1200&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2350&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 50<br>&nbsp;6&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2450&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4800&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 100<br>&nbsp;7&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4900&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 9700&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 100<br>&nbsp;8&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 10200&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 19900&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 500<br>&nbsp;9&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 21200&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 41100&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1300<br>10&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 42400&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 83500&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1300</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img width=\"70%\" class=\"wp-image-1557 b-loaded\" alt=\"骰寶骰子遊戲還是有各種心法和技巧的\" srcset=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/cymd0voyffu-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/cymd0voyffu-300x200.jpg 300w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/cymd0voyffu-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/cymd0voyffu-1200x800.jpg 1200w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/cymd0voyffu-600x400.jpg 600w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/cymd0voyffu-675x450.jpg 675w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/cymd0voyffu.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/cymd0voyffu-1024x683.jpg\">\r\n<figcaption><strong>骰寶技巧：</strong> <strong>三軍10式直纜心法</strong>投注方式</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-ab452adb-5e42-4dec-9bc1-3eb00f840c81\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E6%8A%95%E6%B3%A8%E5%BF%83%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%9A\"></span>投注心法：<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>1、仍然是大數法則，物極必反，前面少了，後面就會多了，大家檢視一下骰寶出數位的記錄就知道，總是密集出號後慢慢變冷，再又慢慢變熱。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>2、因為限注及本金的有限，直纜不可能太長，因此，可以用等待來延長直纜的長度。比如隔3期再用攬，原本的10式纜相當於13式了。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>3、此纜最適合打骰寶的三軍，為什麼？因為打大小遇到圍骰（豹子）會全軍覆沒，打三軍正好相反，遇到出雙數（如225，255）一賠二，圍骰（222，555）一賠三，如果在第8期遇到雙數，<br>&nbsp;利潤是收收回10200*3-累計投注（10200+9700）=10700，有什麼纜能達到這樣的收益率？即使沒遇上雙數或圍骰，也有少少盈利。最大盈利點在於雙數或圍骰，骰寶的雙數是很頻繁的。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>4、三軍的概率如何？骰寶中絕對不出某個數字的概率是5*5*5=125/216，那麼某個數至少出一個的概率是（216-125）/216=91/216=42.12%，這裡面同時出2個或3個某數字只計算一次，如果統計某個數字出現個數占總期數的概率應該是50%（1/6+1/6+1/6=1/2），概率不比大小低了，還沒有圍骰風險。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>4、最重要的是投注切入點，若要萬無一失，選在冷了9期才出的數字，隔二手再用纜。比如數字1，前面9期都沒出，第10期出了，11期和12期不投，如果11~12期都沒出，13期開始以10式直纜跟進，直到中為止。但這樣的投注機會較少，可以降低要求，看到隔5期才出的數字，隔兩期開始追。我統計過，400期中13期不出的現象只有1~2次，但都不是在冷號之後再冷這麼久的。因此，為了繞開13期不出斷纜的悲劇，要觀察以前的記錄中，該數位近期是否開得太密集？雙數要當成連出2期，圍骰當連出3期，如果是稀稀朗朗，則放心大膽地追，如果比較密集，還是不要追吧。為什麼一定要冷號出號之後再追？因為冷號已冷，斷無再長期冷之理。配合此觀察法，即使選隔4期才出的數字追也相當保險，因為變相（隔3期跟進）的直纜長達13期以上，如果不是太太太倒楣，一般都會過關。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>5、為什麼首期要投100？因為在隔二期之後出數比之後出數的頻率都高些， 一中就賺100，否則每次賺50太慢了啊。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>6、為什麼這個直纜沒有第11期？因為我在海立方時，骰寶賭台最高只能賠6萬，所以設計纜時，一是要關注限紅，二是要關注最高賠彩。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--codes_iframe--><!--/codes_iframe-->			</div>\r\n\r\n						</article>\r\n</div> ', '2022-06-07 00:55:42'),
(63, 27, '線上真人雙骰子（Craps）', '投注策略與技巧', NULL, 1, 0, '<div class=\"product\"><article id=\"post-2310\" class=\"post-2310 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail  category-48 single-post-content \">\r\n						<div class=\"post-header post-tp-1-header\">\r\n									<h1 class=\"single-post-title\">\r\n						<span class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">線上真人雙骰子（Craps）投注策略與技巧</span></h1>\r\n										<div class=\"post-meta-wrap clearfix\">\r\n						<div class=\"term-badges \"><span class=\"term-badge term-48\">骰寶技巧教學</span></div>					</div>\r\n									<div class=\"single-featured\">\r\n									</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n						<div class=\"entry-content clearfix single-post-content\">\r\n				<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_22 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-light-blue\">\r\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\r\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">內容目錄</p>\r\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: inline;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"></i></a></span></div>\r\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"#%E7%B7%9A%E4%B8%8A%E7%9C%9F%E4%BA%BA%E9%9B%99%E9%AA%B0%E5%AD%90%EF%BC%88Craps%EF%BC%89%E6%8A%95%E6%B3%A8%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E8%88%87%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7\" title=\"線上真人雙骰子（Craps）投注策略與技巧\">線上真人雙骰子（Craps）投注策略與技巧</a></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-db04b3b3-66d6-4fa3-8f06-8903ae1b4532\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%E7%B7%9A%E4%B8%8A%E7%9C%9F%E4%BA%BA%E9%9B%99%E9%AA%B0%E5%AD%90%EF%BC%88Craps%EF%BC%89%E6%8A%95%E6%B3%A8%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E8%88%87%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7\"></span>線上真人雙骰子（Craps）投注策略與技巧<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-4838 size-large b-loaded\" alt=\"二十一點算牌攻防戰\" width=\"70%\" srcset=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/二十一點算牌攻防戰-1024x678.jpg 1024w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/二十一點算牌攻防戰-300x199.jpg 300w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/二十一點算牌攻防戰-768x508.jpg 768w, https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/二十一點算牌攻防戰.jpg 1328w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://bac88.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/二十一點算牌攻防戰-1024x678.jpg\">\r\n<figcaption>線上真人雙骰子（Craps）投注策略與技巧</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section id=\"uagb-section-de351ab4-c2ec-41be-9584-5a3233ae5e4e\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\">\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\r\n<p>凡是有意瞭解過如今豐富多彩的網上博彩遊戲的人，一般都不會否認雙骰子（Craps）從磚頭加灰漿（現實的）娛樂場中的遊戲非常成功地轉型為網路遊戲，因此很多人都希望掌握雙骰子（Craps）策略的精髓。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>置注機會注-沒有娛樂場收益率顯然，投出這種注就是為了在遊戲允許的情況下贏得賭金，而且不給娛樂場留任何收益。這樣的一種押注，即所謂的置注機會注，只有在您押了過線投注後才可以投。建立某一點數後，您可以根據“機會概率”對您的過線注翻上數倍。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>倍數可以不同，通常都是首次押注的2倍。投出該注後，您期待的就是在7之前再次丟出該點數。置注機會注之所以非常有吸引力，就是因為一旦押中就能贏得更多。您根據機會概率允許的翻倍倍數通常都只有過線注的2倍（點數為4，5，9和10）。但是，如果出現6和8，倍數就可以是過線注的2.5倍。第三種情況就是全額雙機會注，即在對所有其他點數押雙倍之外，還對6或者8的點數再押2.5倍。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>歪打正著與過線投注正好相反的就是不過線投注。如果出場擲是2或3，您就贏；如果丟出7或11，您就輸；此外，丟出12即平局，此時就要重擲骰子直到出現點數或7.您能押贏的就是在點數之前丟出一個7，否則就輸了。押不過線投注的人通常稱為“歪打正著”的人（但是不要因此感覺受挫），這個綽號就是因為您押了不過線注而最後贏了，而其他所有人都輸了，反之亦然。很顯然，如果現實的娛樂場裡、與其他活生生的玩家同台押注時出現歪打正著情況，往往讓人很尷尬，這也能解釋為什麼在網上人們更喜歡押不過線注了。另一種事實情況就是，押不過線注時的娛樂場收益率是1.364％，而且對於賭場抽取來說也比較方便。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>當然，以上部分是您在玩雙骰子時很多種押注情況中的極少出現的，但是，對它們瞭解得越詳細，您就更精通這種遊戲。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--codes_iframe--><!--/codes_iframe-->			</div>\r\n\r\n						</article>\r\n</div>', '2022-06-07 00:55:42'),
