得博牌</span><span class=\"s3\"> 7 </span><span class=\"s1\">不得博牌</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 90px;\">\r\n<td class=\"td1\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 73px; border-style: solid; border-color: #000000; height: 90px;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">8</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"td2\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 103px; border-style: solid; border-color: #000000; height: 90px;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n<p class=\"p3\"><span class=\"s1\">例牌，即定勝負</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"td1\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 36px; border-style: solid; border-color: #000000; height: 90px;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">8</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"td3\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 354px; border-style: solid; border-color: #000000; height: 90px;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n<p class=\"p3\"><span class=\"s1\">例牌，即定勝負</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 90px;\">\r\n<td class=\"td1\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 73px; border-style: solid; border-color: #000000; height: 90px;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">9</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"td2\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 103px; border-style: solid; border-color: #000000; height: 90px;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n<p class=\"p3\"><span class=\"s1\">例牌，即定勝負</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"td1\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 36px; border-style: solid; border-color: #000000; height: 90px;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">9</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"td3\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 354px; border-style: solid; border-color: #000000; height: 90px;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n<p class=\"p3\"><span class=\"s1\">例牌，即定勝負</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>莊閒任何一方兩牌合計8、9點為例牌, 對方不須博牌, 即定勝負。</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>莊閒兩方各得6、7點, 即和局.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>閒家和莊家對點數大小， 點數較大算贏， 買莊家贏1賠1但收5%的傭金，買閒家贏則1賠1，買和局通常賠率為1賠8.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>百家樂除了和局的投注外， 是賭場中最佳投注的賭博遊戲。下表是顯示所有可投注項目中的賭場優勢. 通常和局賠率是1賠8，但有時有1賠9.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<table class=\"t1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"td1\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 566px; border-style: solid; border-color: #000000;\" colspan=\"4\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">百家樂使用八副牌時的機率</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"td2\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 32px; border-style: solid; border-color: #000000; background-color: #52c2ff;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">投注</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"td3\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 319px; border-style: solid; border-color: #000000; background-color: #52c2ff;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">組合</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"td4\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 111px; border-style: solid; border-color: #000000; background-color: #52c2ff;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">機率</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"td5\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 104px; border-style: solid; border-color: #000000; background-color: #52c2ff;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">賭場優勢</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"td2\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 32px; border-style: solid; border-color: #000000; background-color: #52c2ff;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">莊贏</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"td3\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 319px; border-style: solid; border-color: #000000;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">2,292,252,566,437,888</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"td4\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 111px; border-style: solid; border-color: #000000;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">45.86%</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"td5\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 104px; border-style: solid; b